given.definition_2: To yield slightly when a force is applied.

spilt.definition_0: To drop something so that it spreads out or makes a mess; to accidentally pour.
spilt.definition_1: To spread out or fall out, as above.
spilt.definition_2: To drop something that was intended to be caught.

sheen.definition_1: A thin layer of a substance (such as oil) spread on a solid or liquid surface.

spelt.definition_0: To read (something) as though letter by letter; to peruse slowly or with effort.
spelt.definition_1: (sometimes with “out”) To write or say the letters that form a word or part of a word.
spelt.definition_2: To be able to write or say the letters that form words.

paste.definition_0: A soft moist mixture, in particular:
paste.definition_1: A substance that behaves as a solid until a sufficiently large load or stress is applied, at which point it flows like a fluid
paste.definition_2: A hard lead-containing glass, or an artificial gemstone made from this glass.

lefty.definition_1: One who has left-wing political views.

moron.definition_0: A stupid person; an idiot; a fool.
moron.definition_1: A person of mild mental subnormality in the former classification of mental retardation, having an intelligence quotient of 50–70.

tenet.definition_0: An opinion, belief, or principle that is held as absolute truth by someone or especially an organization.

elude.definition_0: To evade, or escape from someone or something, especially by using cunning or skill
elude.definition_1: To shake off a pursuer; to give someone the slip
elude.definition_2: To escape understanding of; to be incomprehensible to

cress.definition_0: (plants) A plant of various species, chiefly cruciferous. The leaves have a moderately pungent taste, and are used as a salad and antiscorbutic.

inlay.definition_0: The material placed within a different material in the form of a decoration.
inlay.definition_1: A filling for a tooth, made of ceramic or gold to fit the cavity and shape of tooth and cemented into place.
inlay.definition_2: The piece of paper or the booklet inside the case of a CD or DVD

eater.definition_2: One who performs fellatio or cunnilingus.

pried.definition_0: To look where one is not welcome; to be nosy.
pried.definition_1: To keep asking about something that does not concern one.
pried.definition_2: To look closely and curiously at (something closed or not public).

tunic.definition_0: A garment worn over the torso, with or without sleeves, and of various lengths reaching from the hips to the ankles.
tunic.definition_1: Any covering, such as seed coat or the organ that covers a membrane.

creek.definition_0: A small inlet or bay, often saltwater, narrower and extending farther into the land than a cove; a recess in the shore of the sea, or of a river; the inner part of a port that is used as a dock for small boats.
creek.definition_1: A stream of water (often freshwater) smaller than a river and larger than a brook.

lance.definition_0: A weapon of war, consisting of a long shaft or handle and a steel blade or head; a spear carried by horsemen.
lance.definition_1: A wooden spear, sometimes hollow, used in jousting or tilting, designed to shatter on impact with the opposing knight’s armour.
lance.definition_2: A spear or harpoon used by whalers and fishermen.

siren.definition_0: One of a group of nymphs who lured mariners to their death on the rocks.
siren.definition_1: One who sings sweetly and charms.

heart.definition_0: A muscular organ that pumps blood through the body, traditionally thought to be the seat of emotion.
heart.definition_1: Emotions, kindness, moral effort, or spirit in general.
heart.definition_2: The seat of the affections or sensibilities, collectively or separately, as love, hate, joy, grief, courage, etc.; rarely, the seat of the understanding or will; usually in a good sense; personality.

diner.definition_1: A dining car in a railroad train.
diner.definition_2: A typically small restaurant, usually modeled after a railroad dining car, that serves lower-class fare, normally having a counter with stools along one side and booths on the other, and often decorated in 50s and 60s pop culture themes and playing popular music from those decades.

dowel.definition_0: A pin, or block, of wood or metal, fitting into holes in the abutting portions of two pieces, and being partly in one piece and partly in the other, to keep them in their proper relative position.
dowel.definition_1: A wooden rod, as one to make short pins from.
dowel.definition_2: A piece of wood or similar material fitted into a surface not suitable for fastening so that other pieces may be fastened to it.

palsy.definition_0: Complete or partial muscle paralysis of a body part, often accompanied by a loss of feeling and uncontrolled body movements such as shaking.

ninja.definition_2: A human, a person of either gender, usually an adult. (See usage notes.)

idiot.definition_0: A person of low general intelligence.
idiot.definition_1: A person who makes stupid decisions; a fool.
idiot.definition_2: A person of the lowest intellectual standing, a person who lacks the capacity to develop beyond the mental age of a normal four-year-old; a person with an IQ below 30.

reply.definition_0: A written or spoken response; part of a conversation.

muddy.definition_1: To make a mess of, or create confusion with regard to; to muddle.

spoil.definition_0: (Also in plural: spoils) Plunder taken from an enemy or victim.
spoil.definition_1: Material (such as rock or earth) removed in the course of an excavation, or in mining or dredging. Tailings.

angle.definition_0: A figure formed by two rays which start from a common point (a plane angle) or by three planes that intersect (a solid angle).
angle.definition_1: The measure of such a figure. In the case of a plane angle, this is the ratio (or proportional to the ratio) of the arc length to the radius of a section of a circle cut by the two rays, centered at their common point. In the case of a solid angle, this is the ratio of the surface area to the square of the radius of the section of a sphere.
angle.definition_2: A corner where two walls intersect.

usual.definition_0: The typical state of something, or something that is typical.
usual.definition_1: A specific good or service (e.g. a drink) that someone typically orders.

ardor.definition_0: Great warmth of feeling; fervor; passion.

stank.definition_0: To have a strong bad smell.
stank.definition_1: To be greatly inferior; to perform badly.
stank.definition_2: To give an impression of dishonesty or untruth.

ditto.definition_0: That which was stated before, the aforesaid, the above, the same, likewise.
ditto.definition_1: A duplicate or copy of a document, particularly one created by a spirit duplicator.

grace.definition_1: A short prayer of thanks before or after a meal.
grace.definition_2: In the games of patience or solitaire: a special move that is normally against the rules.

erupt.definition_0: To eject something violently (such as lava or water, as from a volcano or geyser).
erupt.definition_1: To burst forth; to break out.
erupt.definition_2: To spontaneously release pressure or tension.

jiffy.definition_0: A very short, unspecified length of time.
jiffy.definition_1: A unit of time defined by the frequency of its basic timer – historically, and by convention, 0.01 of a second, but some computer operating systems use other values.
jiffy.definition_2: The length of an alternating current power cycle (1/60 or 1/50 of a second).

chose.definition_0: To pick; to make the choice of; to select.
chose.definition_2: To decide to act in a certain way.

sadly.definition_2: Very much (of a desire etc.); dearly; urgently.

slick.definition_0: A covering of liquid, particularly oil.
slick.definition_1: Someone who is clever and untrustworthy.
slick.definition_2: A tool used to make something smooth or even.

winch.definition_0: A machine consisting of a drum on an axle, a friction brake or ratchet and pawl, and a crank handle or prime mover (often an electric or hydraulic motor), with or without gearing, to give increased mechanical advantage when hauling on a rope or cable.
winch.definition_1: A hoisting machine used for loading or discharging cargo, or for hauling in lines. (FM 55-501).
winch.definition_2: A wince (machine used in dyeing or steeping cloth).

lunar.definition_0: The middle bone of the proximal series of the carpus in the wrist, which is shaped like a half-moon.
lunar.definition_1: An observation of a lunar distance, especially for establishing the longitude of a ship at sea.

birch.definition_0: Any of various trees of the genus Betula, native to countries in the Northern Hemisphere.
birch.definition_1: A hard wood taken from the birch tree, typically used to make furniture.
birch.definition_2: A stick, rod or bundle of twigs made from birch wood, used for punishment.

brawn.definition_0: Strong muscles or lean flesh, especially of the arm, leg or thumb.
brawn.definition_2: Head cheese; a terrine made from the head of a pig or calf; originally boar's meat.

exile.definition_0: The state of being banished from one's home or country.
exile.definition_1: Someone who is banished from their home or country.

still.definition_0: A period of calm or silence.
still.definition_1: A photograph, as opposed to movie footage.
still.definition_2: A resident of the Falkland Islands.

venom.definition_0: A poison carried by an animal, usually injected into an enemy or prey by biting or stinging.
venom.definition_1: Feeling or speech marked by spite or malice; vitriol.

awoke.definition_0: To become conscious after having slept.
awoke.definition_2: To excite or to stir up something latent.

crock.definition_0: A stoneware or earthenware jar or storage container.
crock.definition_1: A piece of broken pottery, a shard.
crock.definition_2: A person who is physically limited by age, illness or injury.

tamer.definition_0: Not or no longer wild; domesticated
tamer.definition_1: (chiefly of animals) Mild and well-behaved; accustomed to human contact

sorry.definition_0: The act of saying sorry; an apology.

reset.definition_0: To set back to the initial state.
reset.definition_2: To adjust; to set or position differently.

purse.definition_0: A small bag for carrying money.
purse.definition_1: A handbag (small bag usually used by women for carrying various small personal items)
purse.definition_2: A quantity of money given for a particular purpose.

chaff.definition_0: The inedible parts of a grain-producing plant.
chaff.definition_1: Straw or hay cut up fine for the food of cattle.
chaff.definition_2: Any excess or unwanted material, resource, or person; anything worthless.

might.definition_0: Power, strength, force or influence held by a person or group.

built.definition_0: To form (something) by combining materials or parts.
built.definition_1: To develop or give form to (something) according to a plan or process.
built.definition_2: To increase or strengthen (something) by adding gradually to.

embed.definition_0: An embedded reporter or journalist, such as a war reporter assigned to and travelling with a military unit, or a political reporter assigned to follow and report on the campaign of a candidate.
embed.definition_1: An element of an advertisement, etc. serving as a subliminal message.
embed.definition_2: An item embedded in another document.

laden.definition_0: To fill or load (related to cargo or a shipment).
laden.definition_1: To weigh down, oppress, or burden.
laden.definition_2: To use a ladle or dipper to remove something (generally water).

goody.definition_0: A good character in a story, often a hero.

kitty.definition_1: (sometimes capitalized) A pet name for a cat.
kitty.definition_2: A money pool, as for a card game, or for shared expenses.

boule.definition_0: One of the bowls used in the French game of boules.
boule.definition_1: A single-crystal ingot produced by synthetic means.

chump.definition_0: To bite or chew loudly or heavily.
chump.definition_1: (Perl) To remove the final character from (a text string) if it is a newline (or, less commonly, some other programmer-specified character).

about.definition_1: In existence; being in evidence; apparent.
about.definition_2: Near; in the vicinity or neighbourhood.

juicy.definition_2: (of a blow, strike, etc.) Strong, painful.

croup.definition_0: An infectious illness of the larynx, especially in young children, causing respiratory difficulty.

dumpy.definition_0: A short, stout person or animal, especially one of a breed of very short-legged chickens.

rabid.definition_0: A human or animal infected with rabies.
rabid.definition_1: Someone who is fanatical in opinion.

scuba.definition_0: (underwater diving) An apparatus carried by a diver, which includes a tank holding compressed, filtered air and a regulator which delivers the air to the diver at ambient pressure which can be used underwater.

swore.definition_0: To take an oath, to promise.
swore.definition_1: To use offensive, profane, or obscene language.

horny.definition_0: Hard or bony, like an animal's horn.

paler.definition_1: (of human skin) Having a pallor (a light color, especially due to sickness, shock, fright etc.).

truce.definition_0: A period of time in which no fighting takes place due to an agreement between the opposed parties
truce.definition_1: An agreement between opposed parties in which they pledge to cease fighting for a limited time

beset.definition_1: (sometimes figurative) To attack or assail, especially from all sides.
beset.definition_2: To decorate something with jewels etc.

edict.definition_0: A proclamation of law or other authoritative command.

ovary.definition_0: A female reproductive organ, often paired, that produces ova and in mammals secretes the hormones estrogen and progesterone.
ovary.definition_1: The lower part of a pistil or carpel that bears ovules and ripens into fruit.

ozone.definition_0: An allotrope of oxygen (symbol O₃) having three atoms in the molecule instead of the usual two; it is a blue gas, generated from oxygen by electrical discharge.
ozone.definition_1: Fresh air, especially that breathed at the seaside and smelling of seaweed.

macaw.definition_0: Any of various parrots of the genera Ara, Anodorhynchus, Cyanopsitta, Orthopsittaca, Primolius and Diopsittaca of Central and South America, including the largest parrots and characterized by long sabre-shaped tails, curved powerful bills, and usually brilliant plumage.

lobby.definition_0: An entryway or reception area; vestibule; passageway; corridor.
lobby.definition_1: That part of a hall of legislation not appropriated to the official use of the assembly.
lobby.definition_2: A class or group of people who try to influence public officials; collectively, lobbyists.

stage.definition_1: A platform; a surface, generally elevated, upon which show performances or other public events are given.
stage.definition_2: A floor or storey of a house.

blink.definition_0: The act of very quickly closing both eyes and opening them again.
blink.definition_1: The time needed to close and reopen one's eyes.
blink.definition_2: A text formatting feature that causes text to disappear and reappear as a form of visual emphasis.

china.definition_0: The plant Smilax china, a liana of much of eastern Asia.

place.definition_0: (physical) An area; somewhere within an area.
place.definition_1: A location or position in space.
place.definition_2: A particular location in a book or document, particularly the current location of a reader.

qualm.definition_0: A feeling of apprehension, doubt, fear etc.
qualm.definition_2: A prick of the conscience; a moral scruple, a pang of guilt. (Now often in negative constructions.)

ridge.definition_0: The back of any animal; especially the upper or projecting part of the back of a quadruped.
ridge.definition_1: Any extended protuberance; a projecting line or strip.
ridge.definition_2: The line along which two sloping surfaces meet which diverge towards the ground.

caddy.definition_0: One hired to assist another in playing the game of golf.

flier.definition_0: That which flies, as a bird or insect.

gnome.definition_0: A brief reflection or maxim; a pithy saying.

snuck.definition_0: To creep or go stealthily; to come or go while trying to avoid detection, as a person who does not wish to be seen.
snuck.definition_1: To take something stealthily without permission.

crook.definition_0: A bend; turn; curve; curvature; a flexure.
crook.definition_1: A bending of the knee; a genuflection.
crook.definition_2: A bent or curved part; a curving piece or portion (of anything).

prose.definition_0: Language, particularly written language, not intended as poetry.
prose.definition_1: Language which evinces little imagination or animation; dull and commonplace discourse.
prose.definition_2: A hymn with no regular meter, sometimes introduced into the Mass.

poppy.definition_0: Any plant of the genus Papaver or the family Papaveraceae, with crumpled, often red, petals and a milky juice having narcotic properties; especially the common poppy or corn poppy (Papaver rhoeas) which has orange-red flowers; the flower of such a plant.
poppy.definition_1: A bright red colour tinted with orange, like that of the common poppy flower.
poppy.definition_2: A simple artificial poppy flower worn in a buttonhole or displayed in other contexts to remember those who died in the two World Wars and other armed conflicts, especially around Remembrance Sunday.

icing.definition_0: A sweet glaze made primarily of sugar and often flavored, typically used for baked goods; frosting.
icing.definition_1: A minor violation of ice hockey rules, occurring when a player shoots the puck from his/her side of the red line so that it crosses the goal line on the opponent's side. A team playing short-handed is not penalized for this.
icing.definition_2: The process of forming a layer of ice on a surface.

scion.definition_0: A descendant, especially a first-generation descendant of a distinguished family.

sushi.definition_0: A Japanese dish made of small portions of sticky white rice flavored with vinegar, usually wrapped in seaweed and filled or topped with fish, vegetables or meat.
sushi.definition_1: Raw fish, especially as a Japanese dish.

sigma.definition_0: The eighteenth letter of the Classical and Modern Greek alphabets, the twentieth letter of Old and Ancient.
sigma.definition_1: The symbol Σ, used to indicate summation of a set or series.
sigma.definition_2: The symbol σ, used to indicate one standard deviation from the mean, particularly in a normal distribution.

fritz.definition_1: (chiefly South Australia) A type of processed meat sausage; devon

verve.definition_0: Excitement of imagination such as that which animates a poet, artist, or musician, in composing or performing

rehab.definition_0: Rehabilitation, especially to treat the use of recreational drugs.

molar.definition_0: A back tooth having a broad surface used for grinding one's food.

flyer.definition_0: That which flies, as a bird or insect.

queue.definition_1: A men's hairstyle whose primary attribute is a braid or ponytail at the back of the head, such as that worn by men in Imperial China.
queue.definition_2: A line of people, vehicles or other objects, in which one at the front end is dealt with first, the one behind is dealt with next, and so on, and which newcomers join at the opposite end (the back).

rebar.definition_0: A steel reinforcing bar in a reinforced concrete structure.
rebar.definition_1: A grid-shaped system of such bars.

hovel.definition_0: An open shed for sheltering cattle, or protecting produce, etc., from the weather.
hovel.definition_1: A poor cottage; a small, mean house; a hut.
hovel.definition_2: In the manufacture of porcelain, a large, conical brick structure around which the firing kilns are grouped.

splat.definition_0: The narrow wooden centre piece of a chair back.

mason.definition_0: A bricklayer, one whose occupation is to build with stone or brick
mason.definition_1: One who prepares stone for building purposes.
mason.definition_2: A member of the fraternity of Freemasons. See Freemason.

whisk.definition_1: A kitchen utensil, made from stiff wire loops fixed to a handle, used for whipping (or a mechanical device with the same function).
whisk.definition_2: A bunch of twigs or hair etc, used as a brush.

spout.definition_0: A tube or lip through which liquid or steam is poured or discharged.
spout.definition_2: The mixture of air and water thrown up from the blowhole of a whale.

dally.definition_0: To waste time in trivial activities, or in idleness; to trifle.
dally.definition_1: To caress, especially of a sexual nature; to fondle or pet
dally.definition_2: To delay unnecessarily; to while away.

ruler.definition_0: A (usually rigid), flat, rectangular measuring or drawing device with graduations in units of measurement; a straightedge with markings.
ruler.definition_1: A person who rules or governs; someone or something that exercises dominion or controlling power over others.

sport.definition_0: Any activity that uses physical exertion or skills competitively under a set of rules that is not based on aesthetics.
sport.definition_1: Something done for fun, regardless of its design or intended purpose.
sport.definition_2: A person who exhibits either good or bad sportsmanship.

bravo.definition_0: A hired soldier; an assassin; a desperado.
bravo.definition_2: The letter B in the ICAO spelling alphabet.

chord.definition_0: A harmonic set of three or more notes that is heard as if sounding simultaneously.
chord.definition_1: A straight line between two points of a curve.
chord.definition_2: A horizontal member of a truss.

stung.definition_0: To hurt, usually by introducing poison or a sharp point, or both.
stung.definition_2: (sometimes figurative) To hurt, to be in pain.

arbor.definition_0: A shady sitting place or pergola usually in a park or garden, surrounded by climbing shrubs, vines or other vegetation.

buddy.definition_1: A partner for a particular activity.
buddy.definition_2: An informal and friendly address to a stranger; a friendly (or occasionally antagonistic) placeholder name for a person one does not know.

range.definition_0: A line or series of mountains, buildings, etc.
range.definition_1: A fireplace; a fire or other cooking apparatus; now specifically, a large cooking stove with many hotplates.

dying.definition_0: To stop living; to become dead; to undergo death.
dying.definition_1: To (stop living and) undergo (a specified death).

ennui.definition_0: A gripping listlessness or melancholia caused by boredom; depression.

betel.definition_0: Either of two plants often used in combination:
betel.definition_1: A quid (chewing preparation) containing these and other plant materials; paan.

genie.definition_0: A jinn, a being descended from the jann, normally invisible to the human eye, but who may also appear in animal or human form.
genie.definition_1: A fictional magical being that is typically bound to obey the commands of a mortal possessing its container.

frisk.definition_0: A frolic; a fit of wanton gaiety; a gambol: a little playful skip or leap.

dwelt.definition_1: To linger (on) a particular thought, idea etc.; to remain fixated (on).
dwelt.definition_2: To be in a given state.

beech.definition_0: A tree of the genus Fagus having a smooth, light grey trunk, oval, pointed leaves and many branches.
beech.definition_1: The wood of the beech tree.

blond.definition_0: A pale yellowish (golden brown) color, especially said of hair color.
blond.definition_1: A person with this hair color.

barge.definition_0: A large flat-bottomed towed or self-propelled boat used mainly for river and canal transport of heavy goods or bulk cargo.
barge.definition_1: A richly decorated ceremonial state vessel propelled by rowers for river processions.
barge.definition_2: A large flat-bottomed coastal trading vessel having a large spritsail and jib-headed topsail, a fore staysail and a very small mizen, and having leeboards instead of a keel.

kiosk.definition_0: A small enclosed structure, often freestanding, open on one side or with a window, used as a booth to sell newspapers, cigarettes, etc.
kiosk.definition_1: A similar unattended stand for the automatic dispensing of tickets, etc.

vista.definition_0: A distant view or prospect, especially one seen through some opening, avenue or passage.
vista.definition_1: A site offering such a view.
vista.definition_2: A vision; a view presented to the mind in prospect or in retrospect by the imagination.

pudgy.definition_0: Fat, overweight (pertaining particularly to children), plump; chubby.

leafy.definition_2: In the form of leaves (of some material)

hotly.definition_1: In a heated manner; intensely or vehemently

noose.definition_0: An adjustable loop of rope, such as the one placed around the neck in hangings, or the one at the end of a lasso.

shied.definition_0: To avoid due to timidness or caution.
shied.definition_2: To throw sideways with a jerk; to fling

daisy.definition_0: A wild flowering plant Bellis perennis of the Asteraceae family, with a yellow head and white petals
daisy.definition_1: Many other flowering plants of various species.

idyll.definition_0: Any poem or short written piece composed in the style of Theocritus' short pastoral poems, the Idylls.
idyll.definition_1: An episode or series of events or circumstances of pastoral or rural simplicity, fit for an idyll; a carefree or lighthearted experience.
idyll.definition_2: A composition, usually instrumental, of a pastoral or sentimental character, e.g. Siegfried Idyll by Richard Wagner.

geeky.definition_0: Resembling or characteristic of a geek.

aunty.definition_0: The sister or sister-in-law of one’s parent.
aunty.definition_1: The female cousin of one’s parent.
aunty.definition_2: A woman of an older generation than oneself, especially a friend of one's parents, by means of fictive kin.

haven.definition_0: A harbour or anchorage protected from the sea.
haven.definition_1: (by extension) A place of safety; a refuge or sanctuary.

stork.definition_0: A large wading bird with long legs and a long beak of the family Ciconiidae.
stork.definition_1: (children's folklore) The mythical bringer of babies to families, or good news.

evict.definition_0: To expel (one or more people) from their property; to force (one or more people) to move out.

cavil.definition_0: A petty or trivial objection or criticism.

excel.definition_0: To surpass someone or something; to be better or do better than someone or something.
excel.definition_1: To be much better than others.

shook.definition_0: A set of pieces for making a cask or box, usually wood.
shook.definition_1: The parts of a piece of house furniture, as a bedstead, packed together.

privy.definition_0: An outdoor facility for urination and defecation, whether open (latrine) or enclosed (outhouse).
privy.definition_1: A lavatory: a room with a toilet.
privy.definition_2: A toilet: a fixture used for urination and defecation.

bongo.definition_0: A striped bovine mammal found in Africa, Tragelaphus eurycerus.

score.definition_0: The total number of goals, points, runs, etc. earned by a participant in a game.
score.definition_1: The number of points accrued by each of the participants in a game, expressed as a ratio or a series of numbers.
score.definition_2: The performance of an individual or group on an examination or test, expressed by a number, letter, or other symbol; a grade.

bluer.definition_2: Pale, without redness or glare; said of a flame.

begun.definition_0: To start, to initiate or take the first step into something.
begun.definition_1: To be in the first stage of some situation

azure.definition_0: A blue colour on a coat of arms, represented in engraving by horizontal parallel lines.
azure.definition_1: The clear blue colour of the sky; also, a pigment or dye of this colour.
azure.definition_2: The unclouded sky; the blue vault above.

weave.definition_0: A type or way of weaving.
weave.definition_1: Human or artificial hair worn to alter one's appearance, either to supplement or to cover the natural hair.

matey.definition_0: The conclusive victory in a game of chess that occurs when an opponent's king is threatened with unavoidable capture.
matey.definition_1: (by extension) Any losing situation with no escape; utter defeat.

braid.definition_0: A sudden movement; a jerk, a wrench.
braid.definition_1: A weave of three or more strands of fibers, ribbons, cords or hair often for decoration.
braid.definition_2: A stranded wire composed of a number of smaller wires twisted together

silky.definition_0: A seal which can magically transform into a human by shedding its skin.

rover.definition_0: (usually in the plural) A randomly selected target.
rover.definition_1: One who roves, a wanderer, a nomad.
rover.definition_2: A vagabond, a tramp, an unsteady, restless person, one who by habit doesn't settle down or marry.

smack.definition_0: A distinct flavor, especially if slight.
smack.definition_1: A slight trace of something; a smattering.

scope.definition_0: The breadth, depth or reach of a subject; a domain.
scope.definition_1: A device used in aiming a projectile, through which the person aiming looks at the intended target.
scope.definition_2: Opportunity; broad range; degree of freedom.

flint.definition_0: A hard, fine-grained quartz that fractures conchoidally and generates sparks when struck.
flint.definition_1: A piece of flint, such as a gunflint, used to produce a spark by striking it with a firestriker.
flint.definition_2: A small cylinder of some other material of the same function in a cigarette lighter, etc.

later.definition_0: Near the end of a period of time.
later.definition_1: Specifically, near the end of the day.
later.definition_2: (usually not comparable) Associated with the end of a period.

woken.definition_0: (often followed by up) To stop sleeping.
woken.definition_1: (often followed by up) To make somebody stop sleeping; to rouse from sleep.
woken.definition_2: To put in motion or action; to arouse; to excite.

globe.definition_2: A spherical model of Earth or any planet.

alive.definition_1: In a state of action; in force or operation; existent
alive.definition_2: Busy with activity of many living beings; swarming; thronged; busy.

rouse.definition_1: The sounding of a bugle in the morning after reveille, to signal that soldiers are to rise from bed, often the rouse.

assay.definition_2: The qualitative or quantitative chemical analysis of something.

poser.definition_0: A particularly difficult question or puzzle.
poser.definition_1: Someone who asks a question or sets a problem.
poser.definition_2: Someone who, or something which, poses; a person who sets their body in a fixed position, such as for photography or painting.

dolly.definition_2: A tool with an indented head for shaping the head of a rivet.

diver.definition_0: Someone who dives, especially as a sport.
diver.definition_1: Someone who works underwater; a frogman.

hazel.definition_0: A tree or shrub of the genus Corylus, bearing edible nuts called hazelnuts or filberts.
hazel.definition_1: The nut of the hazel tree.
hazel.definition_2: The wood of a hazelnut tree.

since.definition_0: From a specified time in the past.

civil.definition_0: Having to do with people and government office as opposed to the military or religion.
civil.definition_1: Behaving in a reasonable or polite manner.
civil.definition_2: Relating to private relations among citizens, as opposed to criminal matters.

jetty.definition_0: A structure of wood or stone extended into the sea to influence the current or tide, or to protect a harbor or beach.
jetty.definition_1: A wharf or dock extending from the shore.
jetty.definition_2: A part of a building that jets or projects beyond the rest, and overhangs the wall below.

anime.definition_0: An artistic style originating in, and associated with, Japanese animation, and that has also been adopted by a comparatively low number of animated works from other countries.
anime.definition_1: An animated work that originated in Japan, regardless of the artistic style.
anime.definition_2: An animated work, regardless of the country of origin.

alley.definition_0: A narrow street or passageway, especially one through the middle of a block giving access to the rear of lots or buildings.
alley.definition_2: An establishment where bowling is played.

choir.definition_0: Singing group; group of people who sing together; company of people who are trained to sing together.
choir.definition_1: The part of a church where the choir assembles for song.
choir.definition_2: (Christian angelology) One of the nine ranks or orders of angels.

outgo.definition_0: The act or process of going out.
outgo.definition_1: A quantity of a substance or thing that has flowed out; an outflow.

clasp.definition_0: A fastener or holder, particularly one that clasps.
clasp.definition_1: (in the singular) An embrace, a grasp, or handshake.

ideal.definition_0: A perfect standard of beauty, intellect etc., or a standard of excellence to aim at.
ideal.definition_1: A subring closed under multiplication by its containing ring.
ideal.definition_2: (lattice theory) A non-empty lower set (of a partially ordered set) which is closed under binary suprema (a.k.a. joins).

spoke.definition_0: A support structure that connects the axle or the hub of a wheel to the rim.
spoke.definition_1: A projecting handle of a steering wheel.

stood.definition_0: (heading) To position or be positioned physically.
stood.definition_1: (heading) To position or be positioned mentally.
stood.definition_2: (heading) To position or be positioned socially.

meant.definition_2: To have conviction in (something said or expressed); to be sincere in (what one says).

hardy.definition_0: (usually in the plural) Anything, especially a plant, that is hardy.
hardy.definition_1: A blacksmith's fuller or chisel, having a square shank for insertion into a square hole in an anvil, called the hardy hole.

bilge.definition_0: The rounded portion of a ship's hull, forming a transition between the bottom and the sides.
bilge.definition_1: The lowest inner part of a ship's hull, where water accumulates.
bilge.definition_2: The water accumulated in the bilge, the bilge water.

seize.definition_0: To deliberately take hold of; to grab or capture.
seize.definition_1: To take advantage of (an opportunity or circumstance).
seize.definition_2: To take possession of (by force, law etc.).

drawl.definition_0: A way of speaking slowly while lengthening vowel sounds and running words together. Characteristic of some southern US accents, as well as Scots.

putty.definition_0: A form of cement, made from linseed oil and whiting, used to fix panes of glass.
putty.definition_1: Any of a range of similar substances.
putty.definition_2: A golf ball made of composition and not gutta-percha.

bosom.definition_0: (somewhat obsolete) The breast or chest of a human (or sometimes of another animal).
bosom.definition_1: The seat of one's inner thoughts, feelings etc.; one's secret feelings; desire.
bosom.definition_2: The protected interior or inner part of something; the area enclosed as by an embrace.

cough.definition_0: A sudden, usually noisy expulsion of air from the lungs, often involuntary.
cough.definition_1: A condition that causes one to cough; a tendency to cough.
cough.definition_2: Used to focus attention on a following utterance, often a euphemism or an attribution of blame

brass.definition_0: A metallic alloy of copper and zinc used in many industrial and plumbing applications.
brass.definition_1: A class of wind instruments, usually made of metal (such as brass), that use vibrations of the player's lips to produce sound; the section of an orchestra that features such instruments
brass.definition_2: Spent shell casings (usually made of brass); the part of the cartridge left over after bullets have been fired.

crick.definition_0: A painful muscular cramp or spasm of some part of the body, as of the neck or back, making it difficult to move the part affected. (Compare catch.)

crump.definition_0: The sound of a muffled explosion.

bathe.definition_0: The act of swimming or bathing, especially in the sea, a lake, or a river; a swimming bath.

burnt.definition_0: To cause to be consumed by fire.
burnt.definition_1: To be consumed by fire, or in flames.
burnt.definition_2: To overheat so as to make unusable.

demur.definition_0: Stop; pause; hesitation as to proceeding; suspense of decision or action; scruple.

elect.definition_1: In Calvinist theology, one foreordained to Heaven. In other Christian theologies, someone chosen by God for salvation.

prime.definition_0: The first hour of daylight; the first canonical hour.
prime.definition_1: The religious service appointed to this hour.

imply.definition_0: (of a proposition) to have as a necessary consequence
imply.definition_1: (of a person) to suggest by logical inference
imply.definition_2: (of a person or proposition) to hint; to insinuate; to suggest tacitly and avoid a direct statement

cabin.definition_0: A small dwelling characteristic of the frontier, especially when built from logs with simple tools and not constructed by professional builders, but by those who meant to live in it.
cabin.definition_1: A chalet or lodge, especially one that can hold large groups of people.
cabin.definition_2: A private room on a ship.

stony.definition_1: Containing or made up of stones.
stony.definition_2: Of a person, lacking warmth and emotion.

trout.definition_0: Any of several species of fish in Salmonidae, closely related to salmon, and distinguished by spawning more than once.

gavel.definition_2: An old Saxon and Welsh form of tenure by which an estate passed, on the holder's death, to all the sons equally.

harem.definition_0: The private part of an Arab household, traditionally forbidden to male strangers.
harem.definition_1: A group of someone's girlfriends, wives and/or concubines in a polygamous household.
harem.definition_2: A group of female animals (cows) herded and controlled by a male animal (bull) of that species for breeding purposes. Such behaviour is exhibited by bovids including cattle and buffalo as well as moose, elephants, seals, sea lions, baboons, and elephant seals.

sworn.definition_0: To take an oath, to promise.
sworn.definition_1: To use offensive, profane, or obscene language.

polyp.definition_0: An abnormal growth protruding from a mucous membrane
polyp.definition_1: A cylindrical coelenterate, such as the hydra, having a mouth surrounded with tentacles

spore.definition_0: A reproductive particle, usually a single cell, released by a fungus, alga, or plant that may germinate into another.
spore.definition_1: A thick resistant particle produced by a bacterium or protist to survive in harsh or unfavorable conditions.

sepia.definition_0: A dark brown pigment made from the secretions of the cuttlefish.
sepia.definition_1: A dark, slightly reddish, brown colour.
sepia.definition_2: (by extension) A sepia-coloured drawing or photograph.

porch.definition_0: A covered and enclosed entrance to a building, whether taken from the interior, and forming a sort of vestibule within the main wall, or projecting without and with a separate roof.
porch.definition_2: The platform outside the external hatch of a spacecraft.

otter.definition_0: An aquatic or marine carnivorous mammal in the subfamily Lutrinae of the family Mustelidae, which also includes weasels, polecats, badgers, and others.
otter.definition_1: A hairy man with a slender physique, in contrast with a bear, who is more thickset.

murky.definition_0: Hard to see through, as a fog or mist.

taper.definition_0: A slender wax candle; a small lighted wax candle
taper.definition_2: A tapering form; gradual diminution of thickness and/or cross section in an elongated object

brave.definition_1: A man daring beyond discretion; a bully.

adopt.definition_0: To take by choice into relationship (a child, heir, friend, citizen, etc.)
adopt.definition_1: To take or receive as one's own what is not so naturally.
adopt.definition_2: To select and take or approve.

fatty.definition_0: Containing, composed of, or consisting of fat.

tread.definition_0: To step or walk (on or over something); to trample.
tread.definition_2: To beat or press with the feet.

hoist.definition_0: A hoisting device, such as pulley or crane.
hoist.definition_1: The act of hoisting; a lift.
hoist.definition_2: The perpendicular height of a flag, as opposed to the fly, or horizontal length, when flying from a staff.

until.definition_0: Up to the time of (something happening).

husky.definition_2: Abounding with husks; consisting of husks.

tuber.definition_0: A fleshy, thickened underground stem of a plant, usually containing stored starch, for example a potato or arrowroot.
tuber.definition_2: A rounded, protuberant structure in a human or animal body.

dingo.definition_0: Canis lupus dingo, a wild dog native to Australia.

amble.definition_0: An unhurried leisurely walk or stroll.
amble.definition_1: An easy gait, especially that of a horse.

villa.definition_0: (plural "villas") A house, often larger and more expensive than average, in the countryside or on the coast, often used as a retreat.
villa.definition_1: (plural "villas") A family house, often semi-detached, in a middle class street.
villa.definition_2: (plural "villae") A country house, with farm buildings around a courtyard.

would.definition_0: Something that would happen, or would be the case, under different circumstances; a potentiality.

copse.definition_0: A thicket of small trees or shrubs.

rabbi.definition_0: A Jewish scholar or teacher of halacha (Jewish law), capable of making halachic decisions.
rabbi.definition_1: A Jew who is or is qualified to be the leader of a Jewish congregation.
rabbi.definition_2: (police) A senior officer who acts as a mentor.

algae.definition_0: Any of many aquatic photosynthetic organisms, including the seaweeds, whose size ranges from a single cell to giant kelps and whose biochemistry and forms are very diverse, some being eukaryotic.

rajah.definition_0: A Hindu prince or ruler in India.
rajah.definition_1: Any of various nymphalid butterflies of the genus Charaxes.

blurb.definition_0: A short description of a book, film, or other work, written and used for promotional purposes.

caste.definition_0: Any of the hereditary social classes and subclasses of South Asian societies.
caste.definition_1: A separate and fixed order or class of persons in society who chiefly associate with each other.
caste.definition_2: A class of polymorphous eusocial insects of a particular size and function within a colony.

gonad.definition_0: A sex organ that produces gametes; specifically, a testicle or ovary.

sassy.definition_0: Bold and spirited, cheeky, impudent, saucy.

clued.definition_1: To provide someone with information which he or she lacks (often used with "in" or "up").

inner.definition_2: A forward who plays in or near the center of the field.

sheet.definition_0: A thin bed cloth used as a covering for a mattress or as a layer over the sleeper.
sheet.definition_1: A piece of paper, usually rectangular, that has been prepared for writing, artwork, drafting, wrapping, manufacture of packaging (boxes, envelopes, etc.), and for other uses. The word does not include scraps and irregular small pieces destined to be recycled, used for stuffing or cushioning or paper mache, etc.
sheet.definition_2: A flat metal pan, often without raised edge, used for baking.

guest.definition_0: A recipient of hospitality, specifically someone staying by invitation at the house of another.
guest.definition_1: A patron or customer in a hotel etc.
guest.definition_2: An invited visitor or performer to an institution or to a broadcast.

angst.definition_1: A feeling of acute but vague anxiety or apprehension often accompanied by depression, especially philosophical anxiety.

mafia.definition_0: A hierarchically structured secret organisation engaged in illegal activities like distribution of narcotics, gambling and extortion.
mafia.definition_2: A trusted group of associates, as of a political leader.

tubal.definition_0: Of or pertaining to a tube, especially an anatomical one

adage.definition_0: An old saying which has obtained credit by long use
adage.definition_1: An old saying which has been overused or considered a cliché; a trite maxim

utile.definition_0: A theoretical unit of measure of utility, for indicating a supposed quantity of satisfaction derived from an economic transaction.

share.definition_0: A portion of something, especially a portion given or allotted to someone.
share.definition_1: A financial instrument that shows that one owns a part of a company that provides the benefit of limited liability.
share.definition_2: A configuration enabling a resource to be shared over a network.

among.definition_0: Denotes a mingling or intermixing with distinct or separable objects. (See Usage Note at amidst.)
among.definition_1: Denotes a belonging of a person or a thing to a group.
among.definition_2: Denotes a sharing of a common feature in a group.

regal.definition_1: Befitting a king, queen, emperor, or empress.

buxom.definition_0: Pliant, obedient, tractable (to) (i.e. easily moved or bent, morally).
buxom.definition_2: Gracious, indulgent, favourable; obliging, amiable, courteous, affable, kindly (as subsense of 1).

pearl.definition_0: A shelly concretion, usually rounded, and having a brilliant luster, with varying tints, found in the mantle, or between the mantle and shell, of certain bivalve mollusks, especially in the pearl oysters and river mussels, and sometimes in certain univalves. It is usually due to a secretion of shelly substance around some irritating foreign particle. Its substance is the same as nacre, or mother-of-pearl. Round lustrous pearls are used in jewellery.
pearl.definition_2: A capsule of gelatin or similar substance containing liquid for e.g. medicinal application.

stilt.definition_0: Either of two poles with footrests that allow someone to stand or walk above the ground; used mostly by entertainers.
stilt.definition_1: A tall pillar or post used to support some structure; often above water.
stilt.definition_2: Any of various wading birds of the genera Himantopus and Cladorhynchus, related to the avocet, that have extremely long legs and long thin bills.

level.definition_0: A tool for finding whether a surface is level, or for creating a horizontal or vertical line of reference.
level.definition_1: A distance relative to a given reference elevation.

posit.definition_0: Something that is posited; a postulate.

sumac.definition_0: Any of various shrubs or small trees of the genus Rhus and other genera in Anacardiaceae, particularly the elm-leaved sumac, Sicilian sumac, or tanner's sumac (Rhus coriaria).
sumac.definition_1: Dried and chopped-up leaves and stems of a plant of the genus Rhus, particularly the tanner's sumac (see sense 1), used for dyeing and tanning leather or for medicinal purposes.
sumac.definition_2: A sour spice popular in the Eastern Mediterranean, made from the berries of tanner's sumac.

shell.definition_0: A hard external covering of an animal.
shell.definition_1: The hard calcareous covering of a bird egg.
shell.definition_2: One of the outer layers of skin of an onion.

shear.definition_0: A cutting tool similar to scissors, but often larger.
shear.definition_1: The act of shearing, or something removed by shearing.
shear.definition_2: Forces that push in opposite directions.

pouch.definition_0: A small bag usually closed with a drawstring.
pouch.definition_1: A pocket in which a marsupial carries its young.
pouch.definition_2: Any pocket or bag-shaped object, such as a cheek pouch.

freak.definition_1: Someone or something that is markedly unusual or unpredictable.

shady.definition_2: Overspread with shade; sheltered from the glare of light or sultry heat.

which.definition_0: (interrogative) What one or ones (of those mentioned or implied).
which.definition_2: (relative) Introduces a relative clause giving further information about something previously mentioned.

amuse.definition_0: To entertain or occupy in a pleasant manner; to stir with pleasing emotions.
amuse.definition_1: To cause laughter or amusement; to be funny.
amuse.definition_2: To keep in expectation; to beguile; to delude.

shank.definition_0: The part of the leg between the knee and the ankle.
shank.definition_1: Meat from that part of an animal.
shank.definition_2: A redshank or greenshank, various species of Old World wading birds in the genus Tringa having distinctly colored legs.

third.definition_0: The person or thing in the third position.
third.definition_1: One of three equal parts of a whole.
third.definition_2: The third gear of a gearbox.

viola.definition_0: A stringed instrument of the violin family, somewhat larger than a violin, played under the chin, and having a deeper tone.
viola.definition_1: An organ stop having a similar tone.
viola.definition_2: A 10-string steel-string acoustic guitar, used in Brazilian folk music.

tutor.definition_0: One who teaches another (usually called a student, learner, or tutee) in a one-on-one or small-group interaction.
tutor.definition_1: A university officer responsible for students in a particular hall.
tutor.definition_2: One who has the charge of a child or pupil and his estate; a guardian.

fancy.definition_1: An image or representation of anything formed in the mind.
fancy.definition_2: An opinion or notion formed without much reflection.

snide.definition_0: An underhanded, tricky person given to sharp practise; a sharper; a cheat.

woody.definition_0: An early station wagon or estate car in which the rear portion of the car's bodywork is made of wood, often associated with Southern California surfing culture.
woody.definition_1: A wooden rollercoaster; an amusement ride whose rails are overlaid upon a wooden track.

sauna.definition_0: A room or a house designed for heat sessions.
sauna.definition_1: The act of using a sauna.
sauna.definition_2: A public sauna; a front for a brothel in some countries.

amass.definition_0: A large number of things collected or piled together.

plane.definition_1: A flat surface extending infinitely in all directions (e.g. horizontal or vertical plane).
plane.definition_2: A level of existence or development. (eg, astral plane)

where.definition_0: The place in which something happens.

frock.definition_0: A dress, a piece of clothing for a female, which consists of a skirt and a cover for the upper body.
frock.definition_1: An outer garment worn by priests and other clericals; a habit.

drunk.definition_0: To consume (a liquid) through the mouth.
drunk.definition_1: (metonymic) To consume the liquid contained within (a bottle, glass, etc.).

steel.definition_0: An artificial metal produced from iron, harder and more elastic than elemental iron; used figuratively as a symbol of hardness.
steel.definition_1: Any item made of this metal, particularly including:
steel.definition_2: Medicinal consumption of this metal; chalybeate medicine; (eventually) any iron or iron-treated water consumed as a medical treatment.

relay.definition_1: A new set of horses kept along a specific route so that they can replace animals that are tired.
relay.definition_2: (by extension) A new set of anything.

halve.definition_0: To reduce to half the original amount.

buyer.definition_0: A person who makes one or more purchases.
buyer.definition_1: (retailing) A person who purchases items for resale in a retail establishment.
buyer.definition_2: A person who purchases items consumed or used as components in the manufacture of products.

lower.definition_0: Situated close to, or even below, the ground or another normal reference plane; not high or lofty.
lower.definition_1: Of less than normal height; below the average or normal level from which elevation is measured.
lower.definition_2: Not high in status, esteem or rank, dignity, or quality. (Compare vulgar.)

array.definition_1: A collection laid out to be viewed in full.
array.definition_2: An orderly series, arrangement or sequence.

modal.definition_1: A modal form, notably a modal auxiliary.

grunt.definition_0: A short snorting sound, often to show disapproval, or used as a reply when one is reluctant to speak.
grunt.definition_1: The snorting cry of a pig.
grunt.definition_2: Any fish of the perciform family Haemulidae.

party.definition_0: A person or group of people constituting a particular side in a contract or legal action.
party.definition_2: A group of people forming one side in a given dispute, contest etc.

sheik.definition_0: The leader of an Arab village, family or small tribe.
sheik.definition_1: An Islamic religious cleric; the leader of an Islamic religious order.
sheik.definition_2: (some Arab Gulf countries) An official title for members of the royal family as well as some prominent families.

missy.definition_0: A young female, or miss; as a term of mild disparagement, typically used jokingly or rebukingly.

clove.definition_0: A very pungent aromatic spice, the unexpanded flower bud of the clove tree.
clove.definition_1: A clove tree, of the species Syzygium aromaticum (syn. Caryophyllus aromaticus), native to the Moluccas (Indonesian islands), which produces the spice.
clove.definition_2: An old English measure of weight, containing 7 pounds (3.2 kg), i.e. half a stone.

ashen.definition_0: Made from the wood of the ash-tree.

vinyl.definition_0: The univalent radical CH2=CH−, derived from ethylene.
vinyl.definition_1: Any of various compounds and substances containing the vinyl radical, especially various tough, flexible, shiny plastics.

trade.definition_0: Buying and selling of goods and services on a market.
trade.definition_1: A particular instance of buying or selling.
trade.definition_2: An instance of bartering items in exchange for one another.

local.definition_0: A person who lives near a given place.
local.definition_1: A branch of a nationwide organization such as a trade union.
local.definition_2: A train that stops at all, or almost all, stations between its origin and destination, including very small ones.

swami.definition_0: (used as a title) A Hindu ascetic or religious teacher.

crest.definition_0: The summit of a hill or mountain ridge.
crest.definition_1: A tuft, or other natural ornament, growing on an animal's head, for example the comb of a cockerel, the swelling on the head of a snake, the lengthened feathers of the crown or nape of bird, etc.
crest.definition_2: The plume of feathers, or other decoration, worn on or displayed on a helmet; the distinctive ornament of a helmet.

frond.definition_0: The leaf of a fern, especially a compound leaf.
frond.definition_1: Any fern-like leaf or other object resembling a fern leaf.

heady.definition_1: Tending to upset the mind or senses.

ramen.definition_0: Soup noodles of wheat, with various ingredients (Japanese style)

junto.definition_0: A group of men assembled for some common purpose; a club, or cabal.

ovoid.definition_0: Something that is oval in shape.

psalm.definition_0: A sacred song; a poetical composition for use in the praise or worship of God.
psalm.definition_1: One of the hymns by David and others, collected into one book of the Old Testament, or a modern metrical version of such a hymn for public worship.

penne.definition_0: A type of short, diagonally cut pasta.

rearm.definition_0: To replace or restore the weapons or arms of a previously defeated, or disarmed army, country, person or other body.

overt.definition_0: Open and not concealed or secret.

hitch.definition_1: Any of various knots used to attach a rope to an object other than another rope.
hitch.definition_2: A fastener or connection point, as for a trailer.

tarot.definition_0: (singular or plural) A card game played in various different variations.
tarot.definition_1: Any of the set of 78 playing cards (divided into five suits, including one of permanent trumps), often used for mystical divination.

credo.definition_1: The liturgical creed (usually the Nicene Creed), or a musical arrangement of it for use in church services.

idler.definition_0: One who idles; one who spends his or her time in inaction.
idler.definition_1: One who idles; a lazy person; a sluggard.
idler.definition_2: Any member of a ship's crew who is not required to keep the night-watch

usage.definition_0: The manner or the amount of using; use.
usage.definition_2: The ways and contexts in which spoken and written words are used, determined by a lexicographer's intuition or from corpus analysis.

bylaw.definition_0: A local custom or law of a settlement or district.
bylaw.definition_1: A rule made by a local authority to regulate its own affairs.
bylaw.definition_2: A law or rule governing the internal affairs of an organization (e.g., corporation or business).

begat.definition_0: An element of a lineage, especially of a lineage given in the Bible

swath.definition_0: The track cut out by a scythe in mowing.
swath.definition_1: A broad sweep or expanse, such as of land or of people.

puree.definition_0: A food that has been ground or crushed into a thick liquid.

realm.definition_0: An abstract sphere of influence, real or imagined.
realm.definition_1: The domain of a certain abstraction.
realm.definition_2: A scope of operation in networking or security.

dryer.definition_0: One who, or that which, dries; a desiccative.
dryer.definition_1: A household appliance that removes the water from clothing by accelerating evaporation, usually though heat and a tumbling motion.

roach.definition_0: Certain members of the fish family Cyprinidae, including:

offer.definition_0: A proposal that has been made.
offer.definition_1: Something put forth, bid, proffered or tendered.
offer.definition_2: An invitation to enter into a binding contract communicated to another party which contains terms sufficiently definite to create an enforceable contract if the other party accepts the invitation.

cyber.definition_0: Everything having to do with the Internet considered collectively.

venue.definition_0: A theater, auditorium, arena, or other area designated for sporting or entertainment events.
venue.definition_1: A neighborhood or near place; the place or county in which anything is alleged to have happened; also, the place where an action is laid, or the district from which a jury comes.
venue.definition_2: A bout; a hit; a turn. See venew.

shalt.definition_0: (modal, auxiliary verb, defective) Used before a verb to indicate the simple future tense in the first person singular or plural.
shalt.definition_1: Used similarly to indicate determination or obligation in the second and third persons singular or plural.
shalt.definition_2: Used in questions with the first person singular or plural to suggest a possible future action.

theta.definition_0: The eighth letter of the Modern Greek alphabet, ninth in Old Greek: Θ, θ.
theta.definition_2: The sensitivity of the value of a derivative with respect to time; the "time decay".

align.definition_0: To form a line; to fall into line.
align.definition_1: To adjust or form to a line; to range or form in line; to bring into line.
align.definition_2: To store (data) in a way that is consistent with the memory architecture, i.e. by beginning each item at an offset equal to some multiple of the word size.

amend.definition_0: (usually in the plural) An act of righting a wrong; compensation.

diary.definition_0: A daily log of experiences, especially those of the writer.
diary.definition_1: A personal organizer or appointment diary.

pixie.definition_0: (fantasy literature, fairy tales) A playful sprite or elflike or fairy-like creature.
pixie.definition_1: A cute, petite woman with short hair.
pixie.definition_2: An upper-atmospheric optical phenomenon associated with thunderstorms, a short-lasting pinpoint of light on the surface of convective domes that produces a gnome.

datum.definition_0: (plural: data) A measurement of something on a scale understood by both the recorder (a person or device) and the reader (another person or device). The scale is arbitrarily defined, such as from 1 to 10 by ones, 1 to 100 by 0.1, or simply true or false, on or off, yes, no, or maybe, etc.
datum.definition_1: (plural: data) A fact known from direct observation.
datum.definition_2: (plural: data) A premise from which conclusions are drawn.

bonus.definition_0: Something extra that is good; an added benefit.
bonus.definition_1: An extra sum given as a premium, e.g. to an employee or to a shareholder.
bonus.definition_2: An addition to the player's score based on performance, e.g. for time remaining.

loyal.definition_0: Having or demonstrating undivided and constant support for someone or something.
loyal.definition_1: Firm in allegiance to a person or institution.
loyal.definition_2: Faithful to a person or cause.

afoot.definition_0: (predicative) That is on foot, in motion, in action, in progress.

topaz.definition_0: A silicate mineral of aluminium and fluorine, usually tinted by impurities.
topaz.definition_1: An often clear, yellowish-brown gemstone cut from this.
topaz.definition_2: A yellowish-brown color, like that of the gemstone.

iliac.definition_0: Of or pertaining to the ilium.

joist.definition_0: A piece of timber laid horizontally, or nearly so, to which the planks of the floor, or the laths or furring strips of a ceiling, are nailed.

timer.definition_1: A device used to measure amounts of time.
timer.definition_2: Any electronic function that causes a device to be able to do something automatically after a preset amount of time.

penal.definition_2: Serving as a place of punishment.

beget.definition_0: To father; to sire; to produce (a child).

slurp.definition_0: A loud sucking noise made in eating or drinking

afoul.definition_0: (principally nautical) In a state of collision or entanglement.
afoul.definition_1: (with of) In a state of entanglement or conflict (with).

knave.definition_0: A boy; especially, a boy servant.
knave.definition_2: A tricky, deceitful fellow; a dishonest person.

savoy.definition_1: An Italian noble family, which became the ruling (hereditary) dynasty of Sardinia and later of Italy
savoy.definition_2: A member of the Savoy noble family

mammy.definition_1: (historical, often pejorative) In the southern United States, a black nanny employed to look after white children; or in the antebellum South, a female slave who was close to the household and looked after the children.

prank.definition_0: A practical joke or mischievous trick.
prank.definition_1: An evil deed; a malicious trick, an act of cruel deception.

chuck.definition_0: Meat from the shoulder of a cow or other animal.
chuck.definition_2: A mechanical device that holds an object firmly in place, for example holding a drill bit in a high-speed rotating drill or grinder.

coral.definition_0: A hard substance made of the limestone skeletons of marine polyps.
coral.definition_2: A somewhat yellowish pink colour, the colour of red coral.

mayor.definition_0: The chief executive of the municipal government of a city, borough, &c., formerly usually appointed as a caretaker by European royal courts but now usually appointed or elected locally.
mayor.definition_1: Short for mayor of the palace, the royal stewards of the Frankish Empire.
mayor.definition_2: Synonym of mair, various former officials in the Kingdom of Scotland.

suing.definition_0: To file a legal action against someone, generally a non-criminal action.
suing.definition_1: To seek by request; to make application; to petition; to entreat; to plead.
suing.definition_2: (of a hawk) To clean (the beak, etc.).

infer.definition_0: To introduce (something) as a reasoned conclusion; to conclude by reasoning or deduction, as from premises or evidence.
infer.definition_1: To lead to (something) as a consequence; to imply. (Now often considered incorrect, especially with a person as subject.)
infer.definition_2: To cause, inflict (something) upon or to someone.

serum.definition_0: The clear yellowish liquid obtained upon separating whole blood into its solid and liquid components after it has been allowed to clot.
serum.definition_1: Blood serum from the tissues of immunized animals, containing antibodies and used to transfer immunity to another individual, called antiserum.
serum.definition_2: A watery liquid from animal tissue, especially one that moistens the surface of serous membranes or that is exuded by such membranes when they become inflamed, such as in edema or a blister.

canon.definition_0: A generally accepted principle; a rule.
canon.definition_1: A group of literary works that are generally accepted as representing a field.
canon.definition_2: The works of a writer that have been accepted as authentic.

stint.definition_0: A period of time spent doing or being something; a spell.
stint.definition_2: Quantity or task assigned; proportion allotted.

drove.definition_0: A number of cattle driven to market or new pastures.
drove.definition_1: (usually in the plural) A large number of people on the move (literally or figuratively).

fishy.definition_0: A cold-blooded vertebrate animal that lives in water, moving with the help of fins and breathing with gills.
fishy.definition_1: Any animal (or any vertebrate) that lives exclusively in water.
fishy.definition_2: The flesh of the fish used as food.

ether.definition_0: The substance formerly supposed to fill the upper regions of the atmosphere above the clouds, in particular as a medium breathed by deities.
ether.definition_1: Often as aether and more fully as luminiferous aether: a substance once thought to fill all unoccupied space that allowed electromagnetic waves to pass through it and interact with matter, without exerting any resistance to matter or energy; its existence was disproved by the 1887 Michelson–Morley experiment and the theory of relativity propounded by Albert Einstein (1879–1955).
ether.definition_2: The atmosphere or space as a medium for broadcasting radio and television signals; also, a notional space through which Internet and other digital communications take place; cyberspace.

apply.definition_0: To lay or place; to put (one thing to another)
apply.definition_1: To put to use; to use or employ for a particular purpose, or in a particular case
apply.definition_2: To make use of, declare, or pronounce, as suitable, fitting, or relative

blunt.definition_0: A fencer's practice foil with a soft tip.
blunt.definition_1: A short needle with a strong point.

bunny.definition_1: A bunny girl: a nightclub waitress who wears a costume having rabbit ears and tail.
bunny.definition_2: In basketball, an easy shot (i.e., one right next to the bucket) that is missed.

poise.definition_0: A state of balance, equilibrium or stability.
poise.definition_1: Composure; freedom from embarrassment or affectation.
poise.definition_2: Mien; bearing or deportment of the head or body.

slang.definition_0: Language outside of conventional usage and in the informal register.
slang.definition_1: Language that is unique to a particular profession or subject; jargon.
slang.definition_2: The specialized language of a social group, sometimes used to make what is said unintelligible to those not members of the group; cant.

shirk.definition_0: One who shirks, who avoids a duty or responsibility.

plunk.definition_0: The dull thud of something landing on a surface.

avail.definition_0: Effect in achieving a goal or aim; purpose, use (now usually in negative constructions).

conch.definition_0: A marine gastropod of the family Strombidae which lives in its own spiral shell.
conch.definition_1: The shell of this sea animal.
conch.definition_2: A musical instrument made from a large spiral seashell, somewhat like a trumpet.

boxer.definition_0: A participant (fighter) in a boxing match.
boxer.definition_1: A breed of stocky, medium-sized, short-haired dog with a square-jawed muzzle.
boxer.definition_2: A type of internal combustion engine in which cylinders are arranged in two banks on either side of a single crankshaft.

space.definition_1: (heading) Unlimited or generalized extent, physical or otherwise.
space.definition_2: (heading) A bounded or specific extent, physical or otherwise.

stole.definition_0: To take illegally, or without the owner's permission, something owned by someone else.
stole.definition_1: (of ideas, words, music, a look, credit, etc.) To appropriate without giving credit or acknowledgement.
stole.definition_2: To get or effect surreptitiously or artfully.

chore.definition_0: A task, especially a difficult, unpleasant, or routine one.

stunt.definition_0: A daring or dangerous feat, often involving the display of gymnastic skills.
stunt.definition_2: A special means of rushing the quarterback done to confuse the opposing team's offensive line.

fluke.definition_0: A lucky or improbable occurrence, with the implication that the occurrence could not be repeated.

puppy.definition_0: A young dog, especially before sexual maturity (12-18 months)

tempo.definition_1: A move which is part of one's own plan or strategy and forces, e.g. by means of a check or attacking a piece, the opponent to make a move which is not bad but of no use for him (the player gains a tempo, the opponent loses a tempo), or equivalently a player achieves the same result in fewer moves by one approach rather than another.
tempo.definition_2: The timing advantage of being on lead, thus being first to initiate a strategy to develop tricks for one's side.

flirt.definition_0: A sudden jerk; a quick throw or cast; a darting motion
flirt.definition_1: Someone who flirts a lot or enjoys flirting; a flirtatious person.

bible.definition_1: A comprehensive manual that describes something. (e.g., handyman’s bible).
bible.definition_2: (at certain US universities) A compilation of problems and solutions from previous years of a given course, used by some students to cheat on tests or assignments.

plate.definition_0: A slightly curved but almost flat dish from which food is served or eaten.
plate.definition_2: The contents of such a dish.

baggy.definition_0: Of clothing, very loose-fitting, so as to hang away from the body.
baggy.definition_1: Of or relating to a British music genre of the 1980s and 1990s, influenced by Madchester and psychedelia and associated with baggy clothing.
baggy.definition_2: Of writing, etc.: overwrought; flabby; having too much padding.

swamp.definition_0: A piece of wet, spongy land; low ground saturated with water; soft, wet ground which may have a growth of certain kinds of trees, but is unfit for agricultural or pastoral purposes.
swamp.definition_1: A type of wetland that stretches for vast distances, and is home to many creatures which have adapted specifically to that environment.
swamp.definition_2: A place or situation that is foul or where progress is difficult.

stake.definition_0: A piece of wood or other material, usually long and slender, pointed at one end so as to be easily driven into the ground as a marker or a support or stay.
stake.definition_1: A piece of wood driven in the ground, placed in the middle of the court, that is used as the finishing point after scoring 12 hoops in croquet.
stake.definition_2: A stick inserted upright in a lop, eye, or mortise, at the side or end of a cart, flat car, flatbed trailer, or the like, to prevent goods from falling off.

bloat.definition_0: Distention of the abdomen from death.
bloat.definition_1: Pathological overdistention of rumen with gas in a ruminant.
bloat.definition_2: Wasteful use of space or other resources.

arose.definition_0: To come up from a lower to a higher position.
arose.definition_1: To come up from one's bed or place of repose; to get up.
arose.definition_2: To spring up; to come into action, being, or notice; to become operative, sensible, or visible; to begin to act a part; to present itself.

mange.definition_0: A skin disease of mammals caused by parasitic mites (Sarcoptes spp., Demodecidae spp.).

maple.definition_0: A tree of the Acer genus, characterised by its usually palmate leaves and winged seeds.
maple.definition_1: The wood of such a tree, prized for its hardness and attractive appearance

meaty.definition_0: Of, relating to, or containing meat.
meaty.definition_2: Of a person or a body part, large and solid.

ester.definition_0: A compound most often formed by the condensation of an alcohol and an acid, with elimination of water, which contains the functional group carbon-oxygen double bond joined via carbon to another oxygen atom.

debit.definition_0: In bookkeeping, an entry in the left hand column of an account.
debit.definition_1: A sum of money taken out of a bank account. Thus called, because in bank's bookkeeping a cash withdrawal diminishes the amount of money held on the account, i.e. bank's debt to the customer.

medal.definition_0: A stamped metal disc used as a personal ornament, a charm, or a religious object.
medal.definition_1: A stamped or cast metal object (usually a disc), particularly one awarded as a prize or reward.

flank.definition_0: The flesh between the last rib and the hip; the side.
flank.definition_1: A cut of meat from the flank of an animal.
flank.definition_2: The extreme left or right edge of a military formation, army etc.

joust.definition_0: A tilting match: a mock combat between two mounted knights or men-at-arms using lances in the lists or enclosed field.

wager.definition_0: Something deposited, laid, or hazarded on the event of a contest or an unsettled question; a bet; a stake; a pledge.
wager.definition_1: That on which bets are laid; the subject of a bet.
wager.definition_2: A contract by which two parties or more agree that a certain sum of money, or other thing, shall be paid or delivered to one of them, on the happening or not happening of an uncertain event.

tramp.definition_0: (sometimes derogatory) A homeless person; a vagabond.
tramp.definition_1: A disreputable, promiscuous woman; a slut.
tramp.definition_2: Any ship which does not have a fixed schedule or published ports of call.

ninth.definition_0: The person or thing in the ninth position.
ninth.definition_1: One of nine equal parts of a whole.
ninth.definition_2: The compound interval between any tone and the tone represented on the ninth degree of the staff above it, as between one of the scale and two of the octave above; the octave of the second, consisting of 13 or 14 semitones (called minor and major ninth).

poesy.definition_1: The class of literature comprising poems; poetry, verse.

forty.definition_0: A bottle of beer containing forty fluid ounces.

oaken.definition_0: Made from the wood of the oak tree. Also in metaphorical uses, suggesting robustness.

gaffe.definition_0: A foolish and embarrassing error, especially one made in public.

waist.definition_0: The part of the body between the pelvis and the stomach.
waist.definition_1: A part of a piece of clothing that covers the waist.
waist.definition_2: The narrow connection between the thorax and abdomen in certain insects (e.g., bees, ants and wasps).

patsy.definition_0: A person who is taken advantage of, especially by being cheated or blamed for something.

truly.definition_0: (manner) In accordance with the facts; truthfully, accurately.

giver.definition_0: One who gives; a donor or contributor.

thief.definition_0: One who carries out a theft.
thief.definition_1: One who steals another person's property, especially by stealth and without using force or violence.
thief.definition_2: A waster in the snuff of a candle.

lemur.definition_0: Any strepsirrhine primate of the infraorder Lemuriformes, superfamily Lemuroidea, native only to Madagascar and some surrounding islands.
lemur.definition_1: Any of the genus Lemur, represented by the ring-tailed lemur (Lemur catta).
lemur.definition_2: A loris (Lemur tardigradus, now Loris tardigradus), predating the 10th edition of Systema Naturæ.

dirge.definition_0: A mournful poem or piece of music composed or performed as a memorial to a dead person.
dirge.definition_1: A song or piece of music that is considered too slow, bland or boring.

lingo.definition_0: Language, especially language peculiar to a particular group, field, or region; jargon or a dialect.

curly.definition_0: A person or animal with curly hair.

cumin.definition_0: The flowering plant Cuminum cyminum, in the family Apiaceae.
cumin.definition_1: Its aromatic long seed, used as a spice, notably in Indian, Middle Eastern, and Mexican cookery.

crypt.definition_1: An underground vault, especially one beneath a church that is used as a burial place.
crypt.definition_2: A small pit or cavity in the surface of an organ or other structure.

deign.definition_0: To condescend; to do despite a perceived affront to one's dignity.
deign.definition_1: To condescend to give; to do something.
deign.definition_2: To esteem worthy; to consider worth notice.

elide.definition_1: To cut off, as a vowel or a syllable.
elide.definition_2: To conflate; to smear together; to blur the distinction between.

posse.definition_0: A group or company of people, originally especially one having hostile intent; a throng, a crowd.
posse.definition_1: A group of people summoned to help law enforcement.

bitty.definition_0: (often in the plural) bitch, girl, woman, especially one that is promiscuous

envoy.definition_0: A short stanza at the end of a poem, used either to address a person or to comment on the preceding body of the poem.

sulky.definition_0: A low two-wheeled cart, used in harness racing.
sulky.definition_1: Any carriage seating only the driver.

koala.definition_0: A tree-dwelling marsupial, Phascolarctos cinereus, that resembles a small bear with a broad head, large ears and sharp claws, mainly found in eastern Australia.

creme.definition_0: A very sugary, fluffy white cream derivative.

duvet.definition_0: A thick, padded quilt used instead of blankets.
duvet.definition_1: A cover for a quilt or comforter.

remit.definition_0: Terms of reference; set of responsibilities; scope.
remit.definition_1: A communication from a superior court to a subordinate court.

nadir.definition_0: The point of the celestial sphere, directly opposite the zenith; inferior pole of the horizon; point of the celestial sphere directly under the place of observation.
nadir.definition_1: The lowest point; time of greatest depression.
nadir.definition_2: The axis of a projected conical shadow; the direction of the force of gravity at a location; down.

least.definition_0: Something of the smallest possible extent; an indivisible unit.

spurn.definition_0: An act of spurning; a scornful rejection.
spurn.definition_1: A kick; a blow with the foot.

rocky.definition_1: In the style of rock music.
rocky.definition_2: Troubled; or difficult; in danger or distress.

mogul.definition_0: A rich or powerful person; a magnate.

bevel.definition_0: An edge that is canted, one that is not a 90-degree angle; a chamfer.

cacti.definition_0: Any member of the family Cactaceae, a family of flowering New World succulent plants suited to a hot, semi-desert climate.
cacti.definition_1: Any succulent plant with a thick fleshy stem bearing spines but no leaves, such as euphorbs.

moody.definition_0: Given to sudden or frequent changes of mind; temperamental.
