chili.definition_0: The pungent, spicy fresh or dried fruit of any of several cultivated varieties of capsicum peppers, used in cooking.
chili.definition_1: Powdered chili pepper, used as a spice or flavouring in cooking.
chili.definition_2: (Indian Chinese cuisine) a spicy stew of chicken or paneer, capsicum and onion, eaten as an appetizer.

facet.definition_0: Any one of the flat surfaces cut into a gem.
facet.definition_1: One among many similar or related, yet still distinct things.
facet.definition_2: One of a series of things, such as steps in a project.

ovate.definition_1: (of leaves) With the broadest extremity near the base.

resin.definition_0: A viscous hydrocarbon secretion of many plants, particularly coniferous trees.
resin.definition_1: Any of various yellowish viscous liquids or soft solids of plant origin; used in lacquers, varnishes and many other applications; chemically they are mostly hydrocarbons, often polycyclic.
resin.definition_2: Any synthetic compound of similar properties.

hotel.definition_0: A large town house or mansion; a grand private residence, especially in France.
hotel.definition_1: An establishment that provides accommodation and other services for paying guests; normally larger than a guesthouse, and often one of a chain.

polar.definition_0: The line joining the points of contact of tangents drawn to meet a curve from a point called the pole of the line.

cleat.definition_0: A strip of wood or iron fastened on transversely to something in order to give strength, prevent warping, hold position, etc.
cleat.definition_1: A continuous metal strip, or angled piece, used to secure metal components.
cleat.definition_2: A device to quickly affix a line or rope, and from which it is also easy to release.

humus.definition_0: A large group of natural organic compounds, found in the soil, formed from the chemical and biological decomposition of plant and animal residues and from the synthetic activity of microorganisms

guilt.definition_1: The state of having been found guilty or admitted guilt in legal proceedings.
guilt.definition_2: The regret of having done wrong.

whole.definition_0: Something complete, without any parts missing.

early.definition_0: A shift (scheduled work period) that takes place early in the day.

salty.definition_2: Coarse, provocative, earthy; said of language.

liner.definition_0: Someone who fits a lining to something.
liner.definition_2: The pamphlet which is contained inside an album of music or movie

stump.definition_0: The remains of something that has been cut off; especially the remains of a tree, the remains of a limb.
stump.definition_1: The place or occasion at which a campaign takes place; the husting.
stump.definition_2: A place or occasion at which a person harangues or otherwise addresses a group in a manner suggesting political oration.

weedy.definition_1: Of, relating to or resembling weeds.

churn.definition_0: A vessel used for churning, especially for producing butter.
churn.definition_1: Customer attrition; the phenomenon or rate of customers leaving a company.
churn.definition_2: The time when a consumer switches his/her service provider.

spoof.definition_0: An act of deception; a hoax; a joking prank.
spoof.definition_2: A drinking game in which players hold up to three (or another specified number of) coins hidden in a fist and attempt to guess the total number of coins held.

witty.definition_1: Possessing a strong intellect or intellectual capacity; intelligent, skilful, ingenious.

troop.definition_0: (collective) A collection of people; a number; a multitude (in general).
troop.definition_1: A small unit of cavalry or armour commanded by a captain, corresponding to a platoon or company of infantry.
troop.definition_2: A detachment of soldiers or police, especially horse artillery, armour, or state troopers.

slept.definition_0: To rest in a state of reduced consciousness.
slept.definition_1: (of a spinning top or yo-yo) To spin on its axis with no other perceptible motion.
slept.definition_2: To cause (a spinning top or yo-yo) to spin on its axis with no other perceptible motion.

agent.definition_0: One who exerts power, or has the power to act
agent.definition_1: One who acts for, or in the place of, another (the principal), by authority from him/her; someone entrusted to do the business of another
agent.definition_2: A person who looks for work for another person

haste.definition_1: Urgency; sudden excitement of feeling or passion; precipitance; vehemence.

debut.definition_0: A performer's first performance to the public, in sport, the arts or some other area.
debut.definition_1: The first public presentation of a theatrical play, motion picture, opera, musical composition, dance, or other performing arts piece.
debut.definition_2: The first appearance of a debutante in society.

crepe.definition_0: A flat round pancake-like pastry from Lower Brittany, made with wheat.
crepe.definition_1: A soft thin light fabric with a crinkled surface.
crepe.definition_2: Crepe paper; thin, crinkled tissue paper.

squib.definition_0: A small firework that is intended to spew sparks rather than explode.
squib.definition_1: A similar device used to ignite an explosive or launch a rocket, etc.
squib.definition_2: A kind of slow match or safety fuse.

probe.definition_0: Any of various medical instruments used to explore wounds, organs, etc.
probe.definition_1: Something which penetrates something else, as though to explore; something which obtains information.
probe.definition_2: An act of probing; a prod, a poke.

annex.definition_1: An appendix to a book or document.
annex.definition_2: An addition or extension to a building.

demon.definition_2: Someone with great strength, passion or skill for a particular activity, pursuit etc.; an enthusiast.

omega.definition_0: The twenty-fourth letter of the Classical and the Modern Greek alphabet, and the twenty-eighth letter of the Old and the Ancient Greek alphabet, i.e. the last letter of every Greek alphabet. Uppercase version: Ω; lowercase: ω.
omega.definition_1: (often capitalized) The end; the final, last or ultimate in a sequence.

spool.definition_0: A reel; a device around which thread, wire or cable is wound, especially a cylinder or spindle.
spool.definition_1: A temporary storage area for electronic mail, etc.

sewer.definition_0: A pipe or system of pipes used to remove human waste and to provide drainage.

morph.definition_0: (grammar) A physical form representing some morpheme in language. It is a recurrent distinctive sound or sequence of sounds.
morph.definition_1: An allomorph: one of a set of realizations that a morpheme can have in different contexts.

spare.definition_0: The act of sparing; moderation; restraint.
spare.definition_2: An opening in a petticoat or gown; a placket.

parse.definition_1: The result of such an act.

admin.definition_1: A systems administrator; one who maintains a computer system or network.
admin.definition_2: A user of a discussion forum, web site, etc. with privileges allowing them to control or restrict the activity of other uses.

pivot.definition_0: A thing on which something turns; specifically a metal pointed pin or short shaft in machinery, such as the end of an axle or spindle.
pivot.definition_1: (by extension) Something or someone having a paramount significance in a certain situation.
pivot.definition_2: Act of turning on one foot.

limit.definition_0: A restriction; a bound beyond which one may not go.
limit.definition_1: A value to which a sequence converges. Equivalently, the common value of the upper limit and the lower limit of a sequence: if the upper and lower limits are different, then the sequence has no limit (i.e., does not converge).
limit.definition_2: Any of several abstractions of this concept of limit.

tabby.definition_0: A kind of waved silk, usually called watered silk, manufactured like taffeta, but thicker and stronger. The watering is given to it by calendering.
tabby.definition_1: A mixture of lime with shells, gravel, or stones, in equal proportions, with an equal proportion of water. When dry, this becomes as hard as rock.

macho.definition_0: A macho person; a person who tends to display masculine characteristics, such as domineering, fierceness, and bravado.
macho.definition_1: The striped mullet of California (Mugil cephalus, syn. Mugil mexicanus).

lousy.definition_0: Remarkably bad; of poor quality, dirty, or underhanded; mean, contemptible.
lousy.definition_2: (usually with with) Filled or packed (with something, usually bad).

revue.definition_0: A form of theatrical entertainment in which recent events, popular fads, etc., are parodied. Any entertainment featuring skits, dances, and songs.

debar.definition_0: To exclude or shut out; to bar.
debar.definition_2: To prohibit (a person or company that has been convicted of criminal acts in connection with a government program) from future participation in that program.

cameo.definition_0: A piece of jewelry, etc., carved in relief.
cameo.definition_1: A single very brief appearance, especially by a prominent celebrity in a movie or song.

tulle.definition_0: A kind of silk lace or light netting, used for clothing, veils, etc.

ethic.definition_0: A set of principles of right and wrong behaviour guiding, or representative of, a specific culture, society, group, or individual.

cairn.definition_0: A rounded or conical heap of stones erected by early inhabitants of the British Isles, apparently as a sepulchral monument.
cairn.definition_1: A pile of stones heaped up as a landmark, to guide travelers on land or at sea, or to arrest attention, as in surveying, or in leaving traces of an exploring party, etc.

sperm.definition_0: The reproductive cell or gamete of the male; a spermatozoon.
sperm.definition_1: Semen; the generative substance of male animals.
sperm.definition_2: Sperm oil; whale oil from a sperm whale; spermaceti.

plank.definition_0: A long, broad and thick piece of timber, as opposed to a board which is less thick.
plank.definition_1: A political issue that is of concern to a faction or a party of the people and the political position that is taken on that issue.
plank.definition_2: Physical exercise in which one holds a pushup position for a measured length of time.

verge.definition_0: A rod or staff of office, e.g. of a verger.

skiff.definition_0: Term used in tea gardens and denotes the act of cutting/pruning the bushes as per the specific norms. Various types of skiff are used viz Light Skiff (LS), Medium Skiff (MS), Deep Skiff (DS) and Level Of Skiff (LOS).

scoop.definition_0: Any cup- or bowl-shaped tool, usually with a handle, used to lift and move loose or soft solid material.
scoop.definition_1: The amount or volume of loose or solid material held by a particular scoop.
scoop.definition_2: The act of scooping, or taking with a scoop or ladle; a motion with a scoop, as in dipping or shovelling.

guide.definition_0: Someone who guides, especially someone hired to show people around a place or an institution and offer information and explanation.
guide.definition_1: A document or book that offers information or instruction; guidebook.
guide.definition_2: A sign that guides people; guidepost.

botch.definition_0: An action, job, or task that has been performed very badly; a ruined, defective, or clumsy piece of work.
botch.definition_1: A patch put on, or a part of a garment patched or mended in a clumsy manner.
botch.definition_2: A mistake that is very stupid or embarrassing.

aisle.definition_0: A wing of a building, notably in a church separated from the nave proper by piers.
aisle.definition_1: A clear path through rows of seating.
aisle.definition_2: A clear corridor in a supermarket with shelves on both sides containing goods for sale.

wrack.definition_0: Vengeance; revenge; persecution; punishment; consequence; trouble.

actor.definition_0: A person who performs, plays a part in a theatrical play or film.
actor.definition_2: One who takes part in a situation.

harpy.definition_0: A fabulous winged monster, ravenous and filthy, having the face of a woman and the body of a vulture.
harpy.definition_2: One who is rapacious or ravenous; an extortioner.

fraud.definition_0: The crime of stealing or otherwise illegally obtaining money by use of deception tactics.
fraud.definition_1: Any act of deception carried out for the purpose of unfair, undeserved and/or unlawful gain.
fraud.definition_2: The assumption of a false identity to such deceptive end.

ghoul.definition_0: (Muslim demonology) A demon said to feed on corpses.
ghoul.definition_2: A person with an undue interest in death and corpses, or more generally in things that are revolting and repulsive.

chard.definition_0: An edible leafy vegetable, Beta vulgaris subsp. cicla, with a slightly bitter taste.
chard.definition_1: Artichoke leaves and shoots, blanched to eat.

gumbo.definition_0: A soup or stew made with okra.
gumbo.definition_1: A fine silty soil that when wet becomes very thick and heavy.

hilly.definition_0: (of a landscape) Abundant in hills; having many hills.

lupus.definition_0: Any of a number of autoimmune diseases, the most common of which is systemic lupus erythematosus.

maker.definition_0: Someone who makes; a person or thing that makes or produces something.
maker.definition_1: (usually capitalized and preceded by the) God.

lipid.definition_0: Any of a group of organic compounds including the fats, oils, waxes, sterols, and triglycerides. Lipids are characterized by being insoluble in water, and account for most of the fat present in the human body.

flunk.definition_0: Of a student, to fail a class; to not pass.
flunk.definition_1: Of a teacher, to deny a student a passing grade.

viper.definition_0: A venomous snake in the family Viperidae.
viper.definition_1: A dangerous, treacherous, or malignant person.

chide.definition_0: To admonish in blame; to reproach angrily.
chide.definition_1: To utter words of disapprobation and displeasure; to find fault; to contend angrily.
chide.definition_2: To make a clamorous noise; to chafe.

booth.definition_0: A small stall for the display and sale of goods.
booth.definition_1: An enclosure just big enough to accommodate one standing person.
booth.definition_2: An enclosed table with seats, as in a diner or café.

mushy.definition_0: Resembling or having the consistency of mush; semiliquid, pasty, or granular.
mushy.definition_2: Overly sappy, corny, or cheesy; maudlin.

voila.definition_0: Lo, there it is; see here; ta-da; presto; behold!

terra.definition_0: (astrogeology) A rough upland or mountainous region of the Moon with a relatively high albedo.

crude.definition_0: Any substance in its natural state.

apart.definition_0: (Used after a noun or in the predicate) Exceptional, distinct.
apart.definition_1: Having been taken apart; disassembled, in pieces.

bound.definition_0: To tie; to confine by any ligature.
bound.definition_1: To cohere or stick together in a mass.
bound.definition_2: To be restrained from motion, or from customary or natural action, as by friction.

older.definition_0: Of an object, concept, relationship, etc., having existed for a relatively long period of time.
older.definition_1: Having been used and thus no longer new or unused.
older.definition_2: Having existed or lived for the specified time.

olden.definition_0: From or relating to a previous era.

drawn.definition_2: (fluidic) To remove or separate or displace.

cheer.definition_0: A cheerful attitude; happiness; a good, happy, or positive mood.
cheer.definition_1: That which promotes good spirits or cheerfulness; provisions prepared for a feast; entertainment.
cheer.definition_2: A cry expressing joy, approval or support such as "hurray".

quest.definition_0: A journey or effort in pursuit of a goal (often lengthy, ambitious, or fervent); a mission.
quest.definition_1: The act of seeking, or looking after anything; attempt to find or obtain; search; pursuit.

broad.definition_0: A shallow lake, one of a number of bodies of water in eastern Norfolk and Suffolk.
broad.definition_1: A lathe tool for turning down the insides and bottoms of cylinders.
broad.definition_2: A British gold coin worth 20 shillings, issued by the Commonwealth of England in 1656.

suite.definition_0: A retinue or company of attendants, as of a distinguished personage
suite.definition_1: A connected series or succession of objects; a number of things used or classed together
suite.definition_2: A group of connected rooms, usually separable from other rooms by means of access.

miner.definition_0: A person who works in a mine.
miner.definition_1: An operator of ordnance mines and similar explosives.
miner.definition_2: Any bird of one of four species of Australian endemic honeyeaters in the genus Manorina.

curse.definition_0: A supernatural detriment or hindrance; a bane.
curse.definition_1: A prayer or imprecation that harm may befall someone.
curse.definition_2: The cause of great harm, evil, or misfortune; that which brings evil or severe affliction; torment.

leant.definition_0: To incline, deviate, or bend, from a vertical position; to be in a position thus inclining or deviating.
leant.definition_1: To incline in opinion or desire; to conform in conduct; often with to, toward, etc.
leant.definition_2: Followed by against, on, or upon: to rest or rely, for support, comfort, etc.

rerun.definition_0: A television program shown after its initial presentation — particularly many weeks after its initial presentation; a repeat.
rerun.definition_1: Another printing run (impression; batch of copies of a given edition) of a book, cartoon, etc.
rerun.definition_2: A political candidate who holds the same political agenda or doctrine as a past or incumbent holder of a given political office.

topic.definition_0: Subject; theme; a category or general area of interest.
topic.definition_2: A musical sign intended to suggest a particular style or genre.

abled.definition_0: (in combination) Having a range of physical powers as specified.

bagel.definition_0: A toroidal bread roll that is boiled before it is baked.
bagel.definition_1: A score of 6-0 in a set (after the shape of a bagel, which looks like a zero).
bagel.definition_2: An overly materialistic and selfish young Jewish man.

mural.definition_0: A large painting, usually drawn on a wall.

crane.definition_0: Any bird of the family Gruidae, large birds with long legs and a long neck which is extended during flight.
crane.definition_1: Ardea herodias, the great blue heron.
crane.definition_2: A mechanical lifting machine or device, often used for lifting heavy loads for industrial or construction purposes.

fifty.definition_0: A banknote or coin with a denomination of 50.
fifty.definition_1: A batsman's score of at least 50 runs and less than 100 runs.

armor.definition_0: A protective layer over a body, vehicle, or other object intended to deflect or diffuse damaging forces.
armor.definition_1: A natural form of this kind of protection on an animal's body.
armor.definition_2: Metal plate, protecting a ship, military vehicle, or aircraft.

brook.definition_0: To use; enjoy; have the full employment of.
brook.definition_2: To bear; endure; support; put up with; tolerate (usually used in the negative, with an abstract noun as object).

began.definition_0: To start, to initiate or take the first step into something.
began.definition_1: To be in the first stage of some situation

legal.definition_0: The legal department of a company.
legal.definition_1: Paper in sheets 8½ in × 14 in (215.9 mm × 355.6 mm).
legal.definition_2: A spy who is attached to, and ostensibly employed by, an embassy, military outpost, etc.

fatal.definition_0: A fatality; an event that leads to death.
fatal.definition_1: A fatal error; a failure that causes a program to terminate.

bossy.definition_0: Tending to give orders to others, especially when unwarranted; domineering.

slant.definition_2: A run: a heading driven diagonally between the dip and strike of a coal seam.

torus.definition_0: A topological space which is a product of two circles.
torus.definition_1: The standard representation of such a space in 3-dimensional Euclidean space: a shape consisting of a ring with a circular cross-section: the shape of an inner tube or hollow doughnut.
torus.definition_2: (in combination, n-torus, 4-torus, etc.) The product of the specified number of circles.

prune.definition_1: The dried, wrinkled fruit of certain species of plum.
prune.definition_2: An old woman, especially a wrinkly one.

scoff.definition_0: Derision; ridicule; a derisive or mocking expression of scorn, contempt, or reproach.
scoff.definition_1: An object of scorn, mockery, or derision.

moral.definition_0: (of a narrative) The ethical significance or practical lesson.
moral.definition_1: (chiefly in the plural) Moral practices or teachings: modes of conduct.

owing.definition_0: To be under an obligation to give something back to someone or to perform some action for someone.
owing.definition_1: To have debt; to be in debt.

covey.definition_1: A brood of partridges, grouse, etc.
covey.definition_2: A party or group (of persons or things).

taken.definition_0: To get into one's hands, possession or control, with or without force.
taken.definition_1: To receive or accept (something) (especially something given or bestowed, awarded, etc).

token.definition_0: Something serving as an expression of something else.
token.definition_2: A piece of stamped metal or plastic, etc., used as a substitute for money; a voucher that can be exchanged for goods or services.

melon.definition_0: Any of various plants of the family Cucurbitaceae grown for food, generally not including the cucumber.
melon.definition_2: A light pinkish orange colour, like that of some melon flesh.

minim.definition_0: A half note, drawn as a semibreve with a stem.
minim.definition_1: A unit of volume, in the Imperial and U.S. customary systems, 1/60 fluid drachm. Approximately equal to 1 drop, 62 μL or 0.9 grain (weight) of water.
minim.definition_2: A short vertical stroke used in handwriting.

ankle.definition_0: The skeletal joint which connects the foot with the leg; the uppermost portion of the foot and lowermost portion of the leg, which contain this skeletal joint.

kneed.definition_1: To poke or strike with the knee.
kneed.definition_2: To move on the knees; to use the knees to move.

odder.definition_0: Differing from what is usual, ordinary or expected.
odder.definition_1: Without a corresponding mate in a pair or set; unmatched; (of a pair or set) mismatched.
odder.definition_2: Left over, remaining after the rest have been paired or grouped.

ebony.definition_0: A hard, dense, deep black wood from various subtropical and tropical trees, especially of the genus Diospyros.
ebony.definition_1: A tree that yields such wood.

clack.definition_0: An abrupt, sharp sound, especially one made by two hard objects colliding repetitively; a sound midway between a click and a clunk.
clack.definition_1: Anything that causes a clacking noise, such as the clapper of a mill, or a clack valve.

elfin.definition_0: An elf; an inhabitant of fairy-land.
elfin.definition_2: Any of the butterflies in the subgenus Incisalia of the North American lycaenid genus Callophrys.

tried.definition_0: Tested, hence, proven to be firm or reliable.
tried.definition_1: Put on trial, taken before a lawcourt.

eager.definition_2: Desirous; keen to do or obtain something.

graph.definition_0: (applied mathematics) A data chart (graphical representation of data) intended to illustrate the relationship between a set (or sets) of numbers (quantities, measurements or indicative numbers) and a reference set, whose elements are indexed to those of the former set(s) and may or may not be numbers.
graph.definition_1: A set of points constituting a graphical representation of a real function; (formally) a set of tuples (x_1, x_2, \ldots, x_m, y)\in\R^{m+1}, where y=f(x_1, x_2, \ldots, x_m) for a given function f: \R^m\rightarrow\R.
graph.definition_2: (formally) An ordered pair of sets (V,E), where the elements of V are called vertices or nodes and E is a set of pairs (called edges) of elements of V; (less formally) a set of vertices (or nodes) together with a set of edges that connect (some of) the vertices.

vicar.definition_0: In the Church of England, the priest of a parish, receiving a salary or stipend but not tithes.
vicar.definition_1: In the Roman Catholic and some other churches, a cleric acting as local representative of a higher ranking member of the clergy.
vicar.definition_2: A person acting on behalf of, or representing, another person.

sixty.definition_0: The cardinal number occurring after fifty-nine and before sixty-one, represented in Roman numerals as LX and in Arabic numerals as 60.

titan.definition_0: Something or someone of very large stature, greatness, or godliness.

leper.definition_1: A person who is shunned; a pariah.

wordy.definition_0: Using an excessive number of words.

nosey.definition_0: A look at something to satisfy one's curiosity.

teary.definition_0: Of a person, having eyes filled with tears; inclined to cry.

bused.definition_0: To transport via a motor bus.
bused.definition_1: To transport students to school, often to a more distant school for the purposes of achieving racial integration.

cobra.definition_0: Any of various venomous snakes of the family Elapidae.

fetal.definition_0: Pertaining to, or connected with, a fetus.

butte.definition_0: An isolated hill with steep sides and a flat top.

uncut.definition_1: (of a gemstone) Not cut or ground to the desired shape.
uncut.definition_2: (of a book) Not having the page edges trimmed.

petal.definition_0: One of the component parts of the corolla of a flower. It applies particularly, but not necessarily only, when the corolla consists of separate parts, that is when the petals are not connately fused. Petals are often brightly colored.

taffy.definition_0: A soft, chewy candy made from boiled molasses or brown sugar.

pouty.definition_0: Tending to pout; angry in a childish or cute way; showing mock anger.

hyena.definition_0: Any of the medium-sized to large feliform carnivores of the subfamily Hyaeninae (genera Hyaena and Crocuta), native to Africa and Asia and noted for the sound similar to laughter which they can make if excited.
hyena.definition_1: (Sub-Saharan Africa) A man that performs ritualized sex acts with recently widowed women and menarchal girls.

dicey.definition_2: Of doubtful or uncertain efficacy, provenance, etc.; dodgy.

weigh.definition_0: To determine the weight of an object.
weigh.definition_1: Often with "out", to measure a certain amount of something by its weight, e.g. for sale.
weigh.definition_2: To determine the intrinsic value or merit of an object, to evaluate.

flame.definition_0: The visible part of fire; a stream of burning vapour or gas, emitting light and heat.
flame.definition_1: A romantic partner or lover in a usually short-lived but passionate affair.
flame.definition_2: Intentionally insulting criticism or remark meant to incite anger.

gypsy.definition_0: (sometimes offensive) A member of the Romani people, or one of the sub-groups (Roma, Sinti, Romanichal, etc).

ladle.definition_0: A deep-bowled spoon with a long, usually curved, handle.
ladle.definition_1: A container used in a foundry to transport and pour out molten metal.
ladle.definition_2: The float of a mill wheel; a ladle board.

broke.definition_0: To separate into two or more pieces, to fracture or crack, by a process that cannot easily be reversed for reassembly.
broke.definition_1: To divide (something, often money) into smaller units.
broke.definition_2: To cause (a person or animal) to lose spirit or will; to crush the spirits of.

ditch.definition_0: A trench; a long, shallow indentation, as for irrigation or drainage.

swoop.definition_0: An instance, or the act of suddenly plunging downward.
swoop.definition_2: A quick passage from one note to the next.

motel.definition_0: A type of hotel or lodging establishment, often located near a major highway, which typically features a series of rooms the entrances of which are immediately adjacent to a parking lot to facilitate convenient access to automobiles parked there.
motel.definition_1: A low-cost short-stay hotel, often with hourly rates rather than daily rates, and notorious for permitting illicit sexual activities; love hotel.

knelt.definition_0: To rest on one's bent knees, sometimes only one; to move to such a position.

debug.definition_0: The action, or a session, of reviewing source code to find and eliminate errors.

awash.definition_0: Washed by the waves or tide (of a rock or strip of shore, or of an anchor, etc., when flush with the surface of the water, so that the waves break over it); covered with water.
awash.definition_1: (by extension) Covered, overspread (with or in something).

baler.definition_0: A machine for creating bales, e.g., of hay or cotton.
baler.definition_1: A person who creates bales, either by operating or feeding such a machine, or by creating the bales by hand.

leapt.definition_1: To pass over by a leap or jump.
leapt.definition_2: To copulate with (a female beast); to cover.

sonar.definition_1: A device that uses hydrophones (in the same manner as radar) to locate objects underwater.

amiss.definition_0: Fault; wrong; an evil act, a bad deed.

myrrh.definition_0: A red-brown resinous material, the dried sap of a tree of the species Commiphora myrrha.

foamy.definition_0: An inexpensive surfboard made of extruded polystyrene foam

rarer.definition_1: (of a gas) Thin; of low density.

binge.definition_0: A short period of excessive consumption, especially of food, alcohol, narcotics, etc.
binge.definition_1: (by extension) A short period of an activity done in excess, such as watching a television show.

imbue.definition_0: To wet or stain an object completely with some physical quality.
imbue.definition_1: In general, to act in a way which results in an object becoming completely permeated or impregnated by some quality.

plaza.definition_1: An open area used for gathering in a city, often having small trees and sitting benches.

funky.definition_1: Not quite right; of questionable quality; not appropriate to the context.

tenor.definition_0: A musical range or section higher than bass and lower than alto.
tenor.definition_1: A person, instrument or group that performs in the tenor (higher than bass and lower than alto) range.
tenor.definition_2: A musical part or section that holds or performs the main melody, as opposed to the contratenor bassus and contratenor altus, who perform countermelodies.

clamp.definition_0: A brace, band, or clasp for strengthening or holding things together.
clamp.definition_1: An instrument used to temporarily shut off blood vessels, etc.
clamp.definition_2: A parking enforcement device used to immobilise a car until it can be towed or a fine is paid; a wheel clamp.

toxic.definition_0: Having a chemical nature that is harmful to health or lethal if consumed or otherwise entering into the body in sufficient quantities.
toxic.definition_1: Appearing grossly unwell; characterised by serious, potentially life-threatening compromise in the respiratory, circulatory or other body systems.

bulge.definition_0: Something sticking out from a surface; a swelling, protuberant part; a bending outward, especially when caused by pressure.
bulge.definition_1: The bilge or protuberant part of a cask.

basil.definition_1: The leaves of this plant used as a herb.
basil.definition_2: Any other species in the genus Ocimum.

macro.definition_0: Very large in scope or scale.

angel.definition_0: An incorporeal and sometimes divine messenger from a deity, or other divine entity, often depicted in art as a youthful winged figure in flowing robes.
angel.definition_1: (Abrahamic tradition) One of the lowest order of such beings, below virtues.
angel.definition_2: A person having the qualities attributed to angels, such as purity or selflessness.

scrum.definition_0: A tightly-packed and disorderly crowd of people.
scrum.definition_1: Specifically used in the Canadian media to describe a tightly-packed group of reporters surrounding a member of the Canadian House of Commons while in the Parliament Buildings.
scrum.definition_2: In rugby union or rugby league, all the forwards joined together in an organised way. Also known as a scrummage.

cadet.definition_0: A student at a military school who is training to be an officer.
cadet.definition_1: A younger or youngest son, who would not inherit as a firstborn son would.
cadet.definition_2: (in compounds, chiefly in genealogy) Junior. (See also the heraldic term cadency.)

tripe.definition_0: The lining of the large stomach of ruminating animals, when prepared for food.
tripe.definition_1: The entrails; hence, humorously or in contempt, the belly; -- generally used in the plural.
tripe.definition_2: (chiefly plural) Something disparaged as valueless, especially written works and popular entertainment (movies, television).

sprig.definition_0: A small shoot or twig of a tree or other plant; a spray.
sprig.definition_1: An ornament resembling a small shoot or twig.
sprig.definition_2: One of the separate pieces of lace fastened on a ground in applique lace.

spine.definition_0: The series of bones situated at the back from the head to the pelvis of a person, or from the head to the tail of an animal; backbone, vertebral column.
spine.definition_1: Something resembling a backbone, such as a ridge, or a long, central structure from which other structures radiate.
spine.definition_2: A pointed, fairly rigid protuberance or needle-like structure on an animal, shell, or plant.

court.definition_0: An enclosed space; a courtyard; an uncovered area shut in by the walls of a building, or by different buildings; also, a space opening from a street and nearly surrounded by houses; a blind alley.
court.definition_2: Attention directed to a person in power; behaviour designed to gain favor; politeness of manner; civility towards someone

maybe.definition_1: An answer that shows neither agreement nor disagreement.
maybe.definition_2: A future event that may or may not happen.

heard.definition_0: (stative) To perceive sounds through the ear.
heard.definition_1: (stative) To perceive (a sound, or something producing a sound) with the ear, to recognize (something) in an auditory way.
heard.definition_2: To exercise this faculty intentionally; to listen to.

cello.definition_0: A large stringed instrument of the violin family with four strings, tuned from lowest to highest C-G-D-A, and played with a bow, also possessing an endpin to support the instrument's weight.

salve.definition_0: An ointment, cream, or balm with soothing, healing, or calming effects.
salve.definition_1: Any remedy or action that soothes or heals.

ounce.definition_0: An avoirdupois ounce, weighing 1/16 of an avoirdupois pound, or 28.3495 grams.
ounce.definition_1: A troy ounce, weighing 1/12 of a troy pound, or 480 grains, or 31.1035 grams.
ounce.definition_2: A US fluid ounce, with a volume of 1/16 of a US pint, 1.8047 cubic inches or 29.5735 millilitres.

scant.definition_1: Not full, large, or plentiful; scarcely sufficient; scanty; meager; not enough.

talon.definition_0: A sharp, hooked claw of a bird of prey or other predatory animal.
talon.definition_1: One of certain small prominences on the hind part of the face of an elephant's tooth.
talon.definition_2: A kind of moulding, concave at the bottom and convex at the top; an ogee. (When the concave part is at the top, it is called an inverted talon.)

limbo.definition_0: (Roman Catholic theology, since circa 400 A.D.) The place where innocent souls exist temporarily until they can enter heaven, notably those of the saints who died before the advent of Christ (limbus patruum) and those of unbaptized but innocent children (limbus infantum).
limbo.definition_1: (by extension, since the 16th century) Any in-between place, state or condition of neglect or oblivion which results in an unresolved status, delay or deadlock.

scowl.definition_0: The wrinkling of the brows or face in frowning; the expression of displeasure, sullenness, or discontent in the countenance; an angry frown.
scowl.definition_1: (by extension) Gloom; dark or threatening aspect.

frail.definition_0: A basket made of rushes, used chiefly to hold figs and raisins.
frail.definition_1: The quantity of fruit or other items contained in a frail.

smote.definition_1: To strike down or kill with godly force.

wafer.definition_1: (christianity) A thin disk of consecrated unleavened bread used in communion.
wafer.definition_2: A soft disk originally made of flour, and later of gelatin or a similar substance, used to seal letters, attach papers etc.

waver.definition_0: An act of wavering, vacillating, etc.
waver.definition_1: Someone who waves, enjoys waving, etc.
waver.definition_2: Someone who specializes in waving (hair treatment).

spark.definition_0: A small particle of glowing matter, either molten or on fire.
spark.definition_1: A short or small burst of electrical discharge.
spark.definition_2: A small, shining body, or transient light; a sparkle.

split.definition_1: A breach or separation, as in a political party; a division.
split.definition_2: A piece that is split off, or made thin, by splitting; a splinter; a fragment.

above.definition_1: Something, especially a person's name in legal documents, that appears higher on the same page or on a preceding page.

baron.definition_0: The male ruler of a barony.
baron.definition_1: A male member of the lowest rank of English nobility (the equivalent rank in Scotland is lord).
baron.definition_2: A particular cut of beef, made up of a double sirloin.

fever.definition_0: A higher than normal body temperature of a person (or, generally, a mammal), usually caused by disease.
fever.definition_1: (usually in combination with one or more preceding words) Any of various diseases.
fever.definition_2: A state of excitement or anxiety.

satyr.definition_0: A woodland creature with pointed ears, legs, and short horns of a goat and a fondness for unrestrained revelry.
satyr.definition_1: Any of various nymphalid butterflies of the genus Faunis.

crime.definition_0: A specific act committed in violation of the law.
crime.definition_1: Any great sin or wickedness; iniquity.

scout.definition_0: A person sent out to gain and bring in tidings; especially, one employed in war to gain information about the enemy and ground.
scout.definition_1: An act of scouting or reconnoitering.
scout.definition_2: A member of any number of youth organizations belonging to the international scout movement, such as the Boy Scouts of America or Girl Scouts of the United States.

flake.definition_0: A loose filmy mass or a thin chiplike layer of anything
flake.definition_1: A scale of a fish or similar animal
flake.definition_2: A prehistoric tool chipped out of stone.

teach.definition_0: To show (someone) the way; to guide, conduct; to point, indicate.
teach.definition_2: To pass on knowledge, especially as one's profession; to act as a teacher.

cleft.definition_0: An opening, fissure, or V-shaped indentation made by or as if by splitting.
cleft.definition_2: A disease of horses; a crack on the band of the pastern.

pinky.definition_0: Methylated spirits mixed with red wine or Condy's crystals.
pinky.definition_1: A baby mouse, especially when used as food for a snake, etc.

chock.definition_0: Any object used as a wedge or filler, especially when placed behind a wheel to prevent it from rolling.
chock.definition_1: Any fitting or fixture used to restrict movement, especially movement of a line; traditionally was a fixture near a bulwark with two horns pointing towards each other, with a gap between where the line can be inserted.

booty.definition_0: A form of prize which, when a ship was captured at sea, could be distributed at once.
booty.definition_1: Plunder taken from an enemy in time of war, or seized by piracy.
booty.definition_2: Something that has been stolen or illegally obtained from elsewhere.

stiff.definition_0: An average person, usually male, of no particular distinction, skill, or education, often a working stiff or lucky stiff.
stiff.definition_1: A person who is deceived, as a mark or pigeon in a swindle.

stave.definition_0: One of a number of narrow strips of wood, or narrow iron plates, placed edge to edge to form the sides, covering, or lining of a vessel or structure; especially, one of the strips which form the sides of a cask, a pail, etc.
stave.definition_1: One of the bars or rounds of a rack, rungs of a ladder, etc; one of the cylindrical bars of a lantern wheel
stave.definition_2: A metrical portion; a stanza; a staff.

anode.definition_0: An electrode, of a cell or other electrically polarized device, through which a positive current of electricity flows inwards (and thus, electrons flow outwards). It can have either a negative or a positive voltage.
anode.definition_1: (by extension) The electrode at which chemical oxidation of anions takes place, usually resulting in the erosion of metal from the electrode.
anode.definition_2: The electrode which collects electrons emitted by the cathode in a vacuum tube or gas-filled tube.

bacon.definition_0: Cured meat from the sides, belly or back of a pig.
bacon.definition_1: Thin slices of the above in long strips.

slunk.definition_1: To give birth to an animal prematurely.

toddy.definition_0: A drink made from alcoholic liquor mixed with sugar, spice and hot water.

mucus.definition_0: A slippery secretion from the lining of the mucous membranes.

coven.definition_0: A formal group or assembly of witches.
coven.definition_1: A family, group or assembly of vampires.
coven.definition_2: A clique that shares common interests or activities.

nylon.definition_0: Originally, the DuPont company trade name for polyamide, a copolymer whose molecules consist of alternating diamine and dicarboxylic acid monomers bonded together; now generically used for this type of polymer.
nylon.definition_1: (in the plural) A stocking originally fabricated from nylon; also used generically for any long, sheer stocking worn on a woman's legs.

papal.definition_0: Having to do with the pope or the papacy.

leggy.definition_0: (chiefly of a woman) Having long, attractive legs; long-legged.
leggy.definition_1: (chiefly of a woman) Exposing the bare or pantyhose-clad legs, especially the thighs.

umbra.definition_0: The fully shaded inner region of a shadow cast by an opaque object.
umbra.definition_1: The central region of a sunspot.

modem.definition_0: A device that encodes digital computer signals into analog/analogue telephone signals and vice versa and allows computers to communicate over a phone line.

livid.definition_2: So angry that one turns pale; very angry; furious.

parka.definition_0: A long jacket with a hood which protects the wearer against rain and wind.

avian.definition_2: (furry fandom) Someone who roleplays or describes themselves as being a bird or bird-like animal character with human characteristics.

beret.definition_0: A type of round, brimless cap with a soft top and a headband to secure it to the head; usually culturally associated with France.

liken.definition_0: (followed by to or unto) To compare; to state that (something) is like (something else).

tonga.definition_0: A light, two-wheeled, horse-drawn carriage used for transportation in India, Pakistan, and Bangladesh.

exert.definition_1: To make use of, to apply, especially of something non-material.

circa.definition_0: Approximately, about, around (typically in relation to time)

etude.definition_0: A short piece of music, designed to give a performer practice in a particular area or skill.

ledge.definition_0: A shelf on which articles may be laid; also, that which resembles such a shelf in form or use, as a projecting ridge or part, or a molding or edge in joinery.
ledge.definition_1: A shelf, ridge, or reef, of rocks.

medic.definition_1: A paramedic, someone with special training in first aid, especially in the military.

raspy.definition_0: (of sound) Rough, raw, especially used to describe vocal quality.

truer.definition_0: (of a statement) Conforming to the actual state of reality or fact; factually correct.
truer.definition_1: Conforming to a rule or pattern; exact; accurate.
truer.definition_2: Of the state in Boolean logic that indicates an affirmative or positive result.

brawl.definition_0: A disorderly argument or fight, usually with a large number of people involved.

tweak.definition_0: A sharp pinch or jerk; a twist or twitch.

wheat.definition_0: Any of several cereal grains, of the genus Triticum, that yields flour as used in bakery.
wheat.definition_1: A light brown colour, like that of wheat.

merry.definition_0: Jolly and full of high spirits.
merry.definition_1: Festive and full of fun and laughter.

women.definition_2: A female person, usually an adult; a (generally adult) female sentient being, whether human, supernatural, elf, alien, etc.

erect.definition_0: Upright; vertical or reaching broadly upwards.
erect.definition_1: (of body parts) Rigid, firm; standing out perpendicularly, especially as the result of stimulation.
erect.definition_2: (of a man) Having an erect penis

purer.definition_0: Free of flaws or imperfections; unsullied.
purer.definition_1: Free of foreign material or pollutants.
purer.definition_2: Free of immoral behavior or qualities; clean.

berry.definition_0: A small succulent fruit, of any one of many varieties.
berry.definition_1: A soft fruit which develops from a single ovary and contains seeds not encased in pits.

axial.definition_0: A flight feather that appears between the primaries and secondaries on some birds.
axial.definition_1: A plane parallel to the surface of a tooth.

brute.definition_0: An animal seen as being without human reason; a senseless beast.
brute.definition_1: A person with the characteristics of an unthinking animal; a coarse or brutal person.
brute.definition_2: (Cambridge University slang) One who has not yet matriculated.

sinew.definition_0: A cord or tendon of the body.
sinew.definition_1: A cord or string, particularly as of a musical instrument.
sinew.definition_2: Muscular power, muscle; nerve, nervous energy; vigor, vigorous strength.

scary.definition_0: Causing or able to cause fright.
scary.definition_2: Subject to sudden alarm; easily frightened.

niche.definition_0: A cavity, hollow, or recess, generally within the thickness of a wall, for a statue, bust, or other erect ornament. Hence, any similar position, literal or figurative.
niche.definition_1: A function within an ecological system to which an organism is especially suited.
niche.definition_2: (by extension) Any position of opportunity for which one is well-suited, such as a particular market in business.

trail.definition_0: The track or indication marking the route followed by something that has passed, such as the footprints of animal on land or the contrail of an airplane in the sky.
trail.definition_1: A route for travel over land, especially a narrow, unpaved pathway for use by hikers, horseback riders, etc.
trail.definition_2: A trailer broadcast on television for a forthcoming film or programme.

daily.definition_0: Something that is produced, consumed, used, or done every day.

carat.definition_0: A unit of weight for precious stones and pearls, equivalent to 200 milligrams.
carat.definition_1: Any of several units of weight, varying from 189 to 212 mg, the weight of a carob seed.
carat.definition_2: A measure of the purity of gold, pure gold being 24 carats.

lumen.definition_0: In the International System of Units, the derived unit of luminous flux; the light that is emitted in a solid angle of one steradian from a source of one candela. Symbol: lm.
lumen.definition_1: The cavity or channel within a tube or tubular organ.
lumen.definition_2: The cavity bounded by a plant cell wall.

mambo.definition_1: A Latin-American musical genre, adapted from rumba, originating from Cuba in the 1940s, or a dance or rhythm of this genre.

taker.definition_1: A person or thing that takes or receives, often more than he or she gives.
taker.definition_2: One who is willing to participate in, or buy, something.

reedy.definition_0: Full of, or edged with, reeds.
reedy.definition_1: (of a sound or voice) High and thin in tone.

clank.definition_0: A loud, hard sound of metal hitting metal.

spasm.definition_0: A sudden, involuntary contraction of a muscle, a group of muscles, or a hollow organ.
spasm.definition_1: A violent, excruciating seizure of pain.
spasm.definition_2: A sudden and temporary burst of energy, activity, or emotion.

kinky.definition_0: Full of kinks; liable to kink or curl.
kinky.definition_1: Marked by unconventional sexual preferences or behavior, as fetishism, sadomasochism, and other sexual practices.

flung.definition_0: To move (oneself) abruptly or violently; to rush or dash.
flung.definition_1: To throw with violence or quick movement; to hurl.
flung.definition_2: To throw; to wince; to flounce.

cagey.definition_1: Uncommunicative; unwilling or hesitant to give information.

bison.definition_1: A similar North American animal, Bison bison.

grimy.definition_1: From the urban musical genre called grime.

stark.definition_1: Severe; violent; fierce (now usually in describing the weather).

gross.definition_1: The total nominal earnings or amount, before taxes, expenses, exceptions or similar are deducted. That which remains after all deductions is called net.
gross.definition_2: The bulk, the mass, the masses.

trump.definition_0: The suit, in a game of cards, that outranks all others.
trump.definition_1: A playing card of that suit.
trump.definition_2: Something that gives one an advantage, especially one held in reserve.

tonic.definition_0: A substance with medicinal properties intended to restore or invigorate.
tonic.definition_2: (Massachusetts) Any of various carbonated, non-alcoholic beverages; soda pop.

satin.definition_0: A cloth woven from silk, nylon or polyester with a glossy surface and a dull back. (The same weaving technique applied to cotton produces cloth termed sateen).

devil.definition_2: A fictional image of a man, usually red or orange in skin color; with a set of horns on his head, a pointed goatee and a long tail and carrying a pitchfork; that represents evil and portrayed to children in an effort to discourage bad behavior.

taboo.definition_0: An inhibition or ban that results from social custom or emotional aversion.
taboo.definition_1: (in Polynesia) Something which may not be used, approached or mentioned because it is sacred.

noise.definition_0: Various sounds, usually unwanted or unpleasant.
noise.definition_1: Sound or signal generated by random fluctuations.

gland.definition_0: An organ that synthesizes a substance, such as hormones or breast milk, and releases it, often into the bloodstream (endocrine gland) or into cavities inside the body or its outer surface (exocrine gland).
gland.definition_1: A secretory structure on the surface of an organ.

reuse.definition_0: The act of salvaging or in some manner restoring a discarded item to yield something usable.
reuse.definition_1: The act of using again, or in another place.

inbox.definition_0: A container in which papers to be dealt with are put.
inbox.definition_1: An electronic folder serving the same purpose.
inbox.definition_2: The aggregate of items that demand one's attention or effort.

dealt.definition_0: To distribute among a number of recipients, to give out as one’s portion or share.
dealt.definition_1: To administer or give out, as in small portions.
dealt.definition_2: To distribute cards to the players in a game.

sauce.definition_0: A liquid (often thickened) condiment or accompaniment to food.
sauce.definition_1: Tomato sauce (similar to US tomato ketchup), as in:

trust.definition_0: Confidence in or reliance on some person or quality.
trust.definition_1: Dependence upon something in the future; hope.
trust.definition_2: Confidence in the future payment for goods or services supplied; credit.

frank.definition_0: Free postage, a right exercised by governments (usually with definite article).
frank.definition_1: The notice on an envelope where a stamp would normally be found.

tract.definition_1: A series of connected body organs, as in the digestive tract.
tract.definition_2: A small booklet such as a pamphlet, often for promotional or informational uses.

surge.definition_0: A sudden transient rush, flood or increase.
surge.definition_1: The maximum amplitude of a vehicle's forward/backward oscillation
surge.definition_2: A sudden electrical spike or increase of voltage and current.

sappy.definition_0: Excessively sweet, emotional, nostalgic; cheesy; mushy. (British equivalent: soppy)
sappy.definition_1: Having (a particularly large amount of) sap.

paddy.definition_0: Rough or unhusked rice, either before it is milled or as a crop to be harvested.
paddy.definition_1: A paddy field, a rice paddy; an irrigated or flooded field where rice is grown.

crush.definition_0: A violent collision or compression; a crash; destruction; ruin.
crush.definition_1: Violent pressure, as of a moving crowd.
crush.definition_2: A crowd that produces uncomfortable pressure.

wooly.definition_0: A sweater or similar garment made of wool.

alloy.definition_0: A metal that is a combination of two or more elements, at least one of which is a metal.
alloy.definition_1: A metal of lesser value, mixed with a metal of greater value.
alloy.definition_2: An admixture; something added which stains, taints etc.

borne.definition_0: To carry or convey, literally or figuratively.
borne.definition_2: To support, keep up, or maintain.

flare.definition_1: A source of brightly burning light or intense heat.
flare.definition_2: A sudden eruption or outbreak; a flare-up.

fried.definition_1: (specifically, of an egg) Fried with the yolk unbroken.
fried.definition_2: Cooked in a deep fryer or pressure fryer or the like after being coated (breaded) in batter; compare deep-fried.

graft.definition_0: A small shoot or scion of a tree inserted in another tree, the stock of which is to support and nourish it. The two unite and become one tree, but the graft determines the kind of fruit.
graft.definition_1: A branch or portion of a tree growing from such a shoot.
graft.definition_2: A portion of living tissue used in the operation of autoplasty.

brunt.definition_0: The full adverse effects; the chief consequences or negative results of a thing or event.
brunt.definition_1: The major part of something; the bulk.

milky.definition_0: Resembling milk in color, consistency, smell, etc.; consisting of milk.
milky.definition_1: (color science) Of the black in an image, appearing as dark gray rather than black.
milky.definition_2: (of a drink) Containing (an especially large amount of) milk.

deuce.definition_0: A card with two pips, one of four in a standard deck of playing cards.
deuce.definition_1: A side of a die with two spots.
deuce.definition_2: A cast of dice totalling two.

welch.definition_0: A person who defaults on an obligation, especially a small one.

baste.definition_0: To sew with long or loose stitches, as for temporary use, or in preparation for gathering the fabric.

miser.definition_0: A person who hoards money rather than spending it; one who is cheap or extremely parsimonious.
miser.definition_1: A kind of earth auger, typically large-bored and often hand-operated.

mirth.definition_0: The emotion usually following humour and accompanied by laughter; merriment; jollity; gaiety.

cabal.definition_0: # A putative, secret organization of individuals gathered for a political purpose.
cabal.definition_2: An identifiable group within the tradition of Discordianism.

pecan.definition_0: A deciduous tree, Carya illinoinensis, of the central and southern United States, having deeply furrowed bark, pinnately compound leaves, and edible nuts.
pecan.definition_1: A smooth, thin-shelled, edible oval nut of this tree.
pecan.definition_2: A half of the edible portion of the inside of this nut.

serif.definition_0: A short line added to the end of a stroke in traditional typefaces, such as Times New Roman.

mower.definition_0: A lawnmower, a machine used to cut grass.

hedge.definition_0: A thicket of bushes or other shrubbery, especially one planted as a fence between two portions of land, or to separate the parts of a garden.
hedge.definition_1: A barrier (often consisting of a line of persons or objects) to protect someone or something from harm.
hedge.definition_2: A mound of earth, stone- or turf-faced, often topped with bushes, used as a fence between any two portions of land.

swash.definition_0: The water that washes up on shore after an incoming wave has broken
swash.definition_1: A long, protruding ornamental line or pen stroke found in some typefaces and styles of calligraphy.
swash.definition_2: A narrow sound or channel of water lying within a sand bank, or between a sand bank and the shore, or a bar over which the sea washes.

flask.definition_0: A narrow-necked vessel of metal or glass, used for various purposes; as of sheet metal, to carry gunpowder in; or of wrought iron, to contain quicksilver; or of glass, to heat water in, etc.
flask.definition_1: A container used to discreetly carry a small amount of a hard alcoholic beverage; a pocket flask.
flask.definition_2: Laboratory glassware used to hold larger volumes than test tubes, normally having a narrow mouth of a standard size which widens to a flat or spherical base.

testy.definition_1: Marked by impatience or ill humor.

fully.definition_0: In a full manner; without lack or defect.
fully.definition_1: In a full degree; to a full extent.

payee.definition_0: One to whom money is paid.

zonal.definition_1: Related to, associated with, or similar to zones.
zonal.definition_2: (of air or ocean currents) roughly longitudinal (east to west, or west to east)

axion.definition_0: A hypothetical subatomic particle postulated to resolve certain symmetry problems concerning the strong nuclear force.

gnash.definition_0: A sudden snapping of the teeth.

pubic.definition_0: Of, or relating to the area of the body adjacent to the pubis or the pubes.

eking.definition_0: The act or process of adding.
eking.definition_2: A supplementary piece of timber used to lengthen another.

dully.definition_0: In a dull manner; without liveliness; without lustre.

cabby.definition_0: A cabdriver; someone who drives a taxi.

endow.definition_0: To provide with a dower or a dowry.
endow.definition_1: To give property to (someone) as a gift; specifically, to provide (a person or institution) with support in the form of a permanent fund of money or other benefits.
endow.definition_2: Followed by with, or rarely by of: to enrich or furnish with some faculty or quality.

geese.definition_0: Any of various grazing waterfowl of the family Anatidae, which have feathers and webbed feet and are capable of flying, swimming, and walking on land, and which are bigger than ducks.
geese.definition_2: The flesh of the goose used as food.

broth.definition_0: Water in which food (meat or vegetable etc) has been boiled.
broth.definition_1: A soup made from broth and other ingredients such as vegetables, herbs or diced meat.

verso.definition_0: The back side of a flat object which is to be examined visually, as for reading, such as a sheet, leaf, coin or medal;
verso.definition_1: The left-hand page of a book of a script which reads from left to right, usually having an even page number.

rotor.definition_0: A rotating part of a mechanical device, for example in an electric motor, generator, alternator or pump.
rotor.definition_1: The wing of a helicopter or similar aircraft.
rotor.definition_2: A quantity having magnitude, direction and position.

madly.definition_0: In a mad manner; without reason or understanding; wildly.

crony.definition_1: Trusted companion or partner in a criminal organization.

anvil.definition_0: A heavy iron block used in the blacksmithing trade as a surface upon which metal can be struck and shaped.
anvil.definition_1: An incus bone in the middle ear.
anvil.definition_2: A stone or other hard surface used by a bird for breaking the shells of snails.

druid.definition_0: One of an order of priests among certain groups of Celts before the adoption of Abrahamic religions.

clone.definition_0: A living organism (originally a plant) produced asexually from a single ancestor, to which it is genetically identical.
clone.definition_1: A group of identical cells derived from a single cell.http//www.medterms.com/script/main/art.asp?articlekey=2754
clone.definition_2: A copy or imitation of something already existing, especially when designed to simulate it.

tenth.definition_0: The person or thing coming next after the ninth in a series; that which is in the tenth position.
tenth.definition_1: One of ten equal parts of a whole.
tenth.definition_2: The interval between any tone and the tone represented on the tenth degree of the staff above it, as between one of the scale and three of the octave above; the octave of the third.

grail.definition_1: The object of an extended or difficult quest.http//www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/grail

drape.definition_1: The way in which fabric falls or hangs.
drape.definition_2: A member of a youth subculture distinguished by its sharp dress, especially peg-leg pants (1950s: e.g. Baltimore, MD). Antonym: square

guise.definition_0: Customary way of speaking or acting; fashion, manner, practice (often used formerly in such phrases as "at his own guise"; that is, in his own fashion, to suit himself.)
guise.definition_1: External appearance in manner or dress; appropriate indication or expression; garb; shape.

fauna.definition_0: Animals considered as a group; especially those of a particular country, region, time.
fauna.definition_1: A book, cataloguing the animals of a country.

relic.definition_0: That which remains; that which is left after loss or decay; a remaining portion.
relic.definition_1: Something old and outdated, possibly kept for sentimental reasons.
relic.definition_2: A part of the body of a saint, or an ancient religious object, kept for veneration.

newly.definition_0: Very recently; in the immediate past.

downy.definition_0: Having down, covered with a soft fuzzy coating as of small feathers or hair.

kayak.definition_0: A type of small boat, covered over by a surface deck, powered by the occupant or occupants using a double-bladed paddle in a sitting position, from a hole in the surface deck

bezel.definition_0: The sloping edge or face on a cutting tool.
bezel.definition_1: The oblique side or face of a cut gem; especially the upper faceted portion of a brilliant (diamond), which projects from its setting.
bezel.definition_2: The rim and flange which encompasses and fastens a jewel or other object, such as the crystal of a watch, in the cavity in which it is set; the collet.

pygmy.definition_0: (often capitalized) A member of one of various Ancient Equatorial African tribal peoples, notable for their very short stature.
pygmy.definition_1: A member of a race of dwarfs.

smith.definition_0: A craftsperson who works metal into desired forms using a hammer and other tools, sometimes heating the metal to make it more workable, especially a blacksmith.
smith.definition_1: (by extension) One who makes anything; wright.

shorn.definition_0: To cut, originally with a sword or other bladed weapon, now usually with shears, or as if using shears.
shorn.definition_1: To remove the fleece from a sheep etc by clipping.
shorn.definition_2: To deform because of forces pushing in opposite directions.

moose.definition_0: The largest member of the deer family (Alces americanus, sometimes included in Alces alces), of which the male has very large, palmate antlers.

biddy.definition_0: A woman, especially an old woman; especially one regarded as fussy or mean or a gossipy busybody.

froze.definition_0: Especially of a liquid, to become solid due to low temperature.
froze.definition_1: To lower something's temperature to the point that it freezes or becomes hard.
froze.definition_2: To drop to a temperature below zero degrees celsius, where water turns to ice.

munch.definition_0: A location or restaurant where good eating can be expected.

wring.definition_0: A powerful squeezing or twisting action.

guppy.definition_0: A tiny freshwater fish, Poecilia reticulata, popular in home aquariums, that usually has a plain body and black or dark blue tail for the females and a more colorful tail for the males.
guppy.definition_2: A tube holding paintballs before they are loaded into the gun.

fifth.definition_0: The person or thing in the fifth position.
fifth.definition_1: One of five equal parts of a whole.
fifth.definition_2: The fifth gear of an engine.

vegan.definition_0: A person who does not eat, drink or otherwise consume any animal products
vegan.definition_1: A person committed to avoiding products and practices that inherently involve animal use, including all foods containing animal products, and to abstaining from direct and intentional harm to animals as far as possible; an adherent to veganism.

nasal.definition_0: A medicine that operates through the nose; an errhine.
nasal.definition_1: A vowel or consonant (such as [m] or [n]) articulated with air flowing through the nose.
nasal.definition_2: Part of a helmet projecting to protect the nose; a nose guard.

newer.definition_2: Current or later, as opposed to former.

antic.definition_0: A grotesque representation of a figure; a gargoyle.
antic.definition_2: (often in plural) A ludicrous gesture or act; ridiculous behaviour; caper.

mamma.definition_0: The milk-secreting organ of female humans and other mammals which includes the mammary gland and the nipple or teat; a breast; an udder. (plural: mammae)
mamma.definition_1: An accessory cloud like a mammary in appearance, which can form on the underside of most cloud genera

banjo.definition_0: A stringed musical instrument (chordophone), usually with a round body, a membrane-like soundboard and a fretted neck, played by plucking or strumming the strings.
banjo.definition_1: Any of various similar musical instruments, such as the Tuvan doshpuluur, with a membrane-like soundboard.
banjo.definition_2: An object shaped like a banjo, especially a frying pan or a shovel.

lorry.definition_0: A motor vehicle for transporting goods, and in some cases people; a truck.
lorry.definition_1: A barrow or truck for shifting baggage, as at railway stations.
lorry.definition_2: A small cart or wagon used on the tramways in mines to carry coal or rubbish.

image.definition_0: An optical or other representation of a real object; a graphic; a picture.
image.definition_1: A mental picture of something not real or not present.

metro.definition_1: A train that runs on such an underground railway.
metro.definition_2: An urban rapid transit light railway

clang.definition_0: A loud, ringing sound, like that made by free-hanging metal objects striking each other.
clang.definition_2: The cry of some birds, including the crane and the goose.

drive.definition_0: Motivation to do or achieve something; ability coupled with ambition.
drive.definition_1: Violent or rapid motion; a rushing onward or away; especially, a forced or hurried dispatch of business.
drive.definition_2: An act of driving animals forward, as to be captured, hunted etc.

thong.definition_1: (usually in the plural) An item of footwear, usually of rubber, secured by two straps which join to pass between the big toe and its neighbour.
thong.definition_2: An undergarment or swimwear consisting of very narrow strips designed to cover just the genitals and nothing more.

scene.definition_0: The location of an event that attracts attention.
scene.definition_2: The decorations; furnishings and backgrounds of a stage, representing the place in which the action of a play is set

exact.definition_0: To demand and enforce the payment or performance of, sometimes in a forcible or imperious way.
exact.definition_2: To inflict; to forcibly obtain or produce.

known.definition_0: To perceive the truth or factuality of; to be certain of or that.
known.definition_1: To be aware of; to be cognizant of.
known.definition_2: To be acquainted or familiar with; to have encountered.

dried.definition_0: Without water or moisture, said of something that has previously been wet or moist; resulting from the process of drying.
dried.definition_1: Usually of foods: cured, preserved by drying.

bunch.definition_0: A group of similar things, either growing together, or in a cluster or clump, usually fastened together.
bunch.definition_1: The peloton; the main group of riders formed during a race.

repel.definition_0: To turn (someone) away from a privilege, right, job, etc.
repel.definition_1: To reject, put off (a request, demand etc.).
repel.definition_2: To ward off (a malignant influence, attack etc.).

gauge.definition_0: A measure; a standard of measure; an instrument to determine dimensions, distance, or capacity; a standard

crack.definition_0: A thin and usually jagged space opened in a previously solid material.
crack.definition_2: A sharply humorous comment; a wisecrack.

latte.definition_0: A drink of coffee made from espresso and steamed milk, generally topped with foam.
latte.definition_1: A similar drink, where the espresso is replaced with some other flavoring ingredient such as chai, maté or matcha (green tea).

cried.definition_1: To utter loudly; to call out; to declare publicly.

stunk.definition_0: To have a strong bad smell.
stunk.definition_1: To be greatly inferior; to perform badly.
stunk.definition_2: To give an impression of dishonesty or untruth.

spear.definition_0: A long stick with a sharp tip used as a weapon for throwing or thrusting, or anything used to make a thrusting motion.
spear.definition_1: A soldier armed with such a weapon; a spearman.
spear.definition_2: A lance with barbed prongs, used by fishermen to retrieve fish.

drown.definition_0: To die from suffocation while immersed in water or other fluid.
drown.definition_1: To kill by suffocating in water or another liquid.
drown.definition_2: To be flooded: to be inundated with or submerged in (literally) water or (figuratively) other things; to be overwhelmed.

chime.definition_0: A musical instrument producing a sound when struck, similar to a bell (e.g. a tubular metal bar) or actually a bell. Often used in the plural to refer to the set: the chimes.
chime.definition_1: An individual ringing component of such a set.
chime.definition_2: A small bell or other ringing or tone-making device as a component of some other device.

setup.definition_0: Equipment designed for a particular purpose; an apparatus.
setup.definition_1: The fashion in which something is organized or arranged.
setup.definition_2: A situation orchestrated to frame someone; a covert effort to place the blame on somebody.

email.definition_0: A system for transferring messages from one computer to another, usually through a network.
email.definition_1: A quantity of messages sent through an email system.
email.definition_2: A message sent through an email system.

folio.definition_0: A leaf of a book or manuscript
folio.definition_1: A page of a book, that is, one side of a leaf of a book.
folio.definition_2: A page number. The even folios are on the left-hand pages and the odd folios on the right-hand pages.

happy.definition_0: A happy event, thing, person, etc.

guava.definition_0: A tropical tree or shrub of the myrtle family, Psidium guajava.
guava.definition_1: Its yellowish tropical fruit, 1¼ to 2 inches, globular or pear-shaped with thin, yellow, green or brown skin, is often made into jams and jellies. The meat is yellowish or pale green to pink in color.
guava.definition_2: A medium reddish-pink colour, like that of guava flesh (also called guava pink).

alibi.definition_0: The plea or mode of defense under which a person on trial for a crime proves or attempts to prove being in another place when the alleged act was committed

femur.definition_1: The middle segment of the leg of an insect, between the trochanter and the tibia.
femur.definition_2: A segment of the leg of an arachnid.

thrum.definition_0: A thrumming sound; a hum or vibration.

petty.definition_0: (usually in the plural) A little schoolboy, either in grade or size.
petty.definition_1: A class or school for young schoolboys.
petty.definition_2: An outhouse: an outbuilding used as a lavatory.

whine.definition_0: A long-drawn, high-pitched complaining cry or sound

fudge.definition_0: A type of very sweet candy or confection, usually made from sugar, butter, and milk or cream. Often used in the US synonymously with chocolate fudge.
fudge.definition_2: A deliberately misleading or vague answer.

wiser.definition_0: Showing good judgement or the benefit of experience.

junta.definition_0: A council, convention, tribunal or assembly; especially, the grand council of state in Spain.
junta.definition_1: The ruling council of a military dictatorship.

impel.definition_0: To urge a person; to press on; to incite to action or motion via intrinsic motivation.
impel.definition_1: To drive forward; to propel an object, to provide an impetus for motion or action.

whose.definition_0: (interrogative) That or those of whom or belonging to whom.
whose.definition_1: (relative) That or those of whom or belonging to whom.

visor.definition_0: A part of a helmet, arranged so as to lift or open, and so show the face. The openings for seeing and breathing are generally in it.
visor.definition_2: The fore piece of a cap, projecting over, and protecting the eyes.

staid.definition_0: Not capricious or impulsive; sedate, serious, sober.
staid.definition_1: Always fixed in the same location; stationary.

mangy.definition_1: (by extension) Worn and squalid-looking; bedraggled or decrepit.

crone.definition_1: An archetypal figure, a Wise Woman.
crone.definition_2: An ugly, evil-looking, or frightening old woman; a hag.

chirp.definition_0: A short, sharp or high note or noise, as of a bird or insect.
chirp.definition_1: (radar, sonar, radio telescopy etc.) A pulse of signal whose frequency sweeps through a band of frequencies for the duration of the pulse.

forte.definition_1: The strong part of a sword blade, close to the hilt.

plait.definition_0: A flat fold; a doubling, as of cloth; a pleat.
plait.definition_1: A braid, as of hair or straw; a plat.

manly.definition_0: Having the characteristics of a man.
manly.definition_1: Having qualities befitting a man; courageous, resolute, noble.

undid.definition_0: To reverse the effects of an action.
undid.definition_2: To impoverish or ruin, as in reputation; to cause the downfall of.

rodeo.definition_0: A gathering of cattle to be branded.
rodeo.definition_1: A North American sport involving skills with horses, cows and other livestock.
rodeo.definition_2: An entertainment event associated with the sport.

peril.definition_0: A situation of serious and immediate danger.
peril.definition_1: Something that causes, contains, or presents danger.
peril.definition_2: An event which causes a loss, or the risk of a specific such event.

spied.definition_1: To spot; to catch sight of.

ripen.definition_0: To grow ripe; to become mature (said of grain, fruit, flowers etc.)
ripen.definition_1: To approach or come to perfection.
ripen.definition_2: To cause to mature; to make ripe

bigot.definition_0: One who is narrow-mindedly devoted to one's own ideas and groups, and intolerant of (people of) differing ideas, races, genders, religions, politics, etc.
bigot.definition_1: One who is overly pious in matters of religion, often hypocritically or else superstitiously so.

snore.definition_0: The act of snoring, and the noise produced.
snore.definition_1: An extremely boring person or event.

teddy.definition_1: A type of all-in-one piece of women's underwear.

intro.definition_1: The opening sequence at beginning of a film, television program, etc.
intro.definition_2: A small demo produced to promote one's demogroup or for a competition.

pulse.definition_0: A normally regular beat felt when arteries are depressed, caused by the pumping action of the heart.
pulse.definition_2: The beat or tactus of a piece of music.

scree.definition_0: Loose stony debris on a slope.
scree.definition_1: (by extension) Similar debris made up of broken building material such as bricks, concrete, etc.
scree.definition_2: A slope made up of loose stony debris at the base of a cliff, mountain, etc.

stash.definition_0: A collection, sometimes hidden; a reserve.
stash.definition_1: A place where drugs are stored.

gourd.definition_0: Any of the trailing or climbing vines producing fruit with a hard rind or shell, from the genera Lagenaria and Cucurbita (in Cucurbitaceae).
gourd.definition_1: A hard-shelled fruit from a plant in Lagenaria or Cucurbita.
gourd.definition_2: The dried and hardened shell of such fruit, made into a drinking vessel, bowl, spoon, or other objects designed for use or decoration.

speak.definition_0: A low class bar, a speakeasy.

pinch.definition_0: The action of squeezing a small amount of a person's skin and flesh, making it hurt.
pinch.definition_1: A close compression of anything with the fingers.
pinch.definition_2: A small amount of powder or granules, such that the amount could be held between fingertip and thumb tip.

polka.definition_0: A lively dance originating in Bohemia.

loamy.definition_0: Consisting of loam; partaking of the nature of loam; resembling loam.

torso.definition_0: The main part of the (human) body that extends from the neck to the groin, excluding the head and limbs.

catty.definition_0: (of a person or remark) With subtle hostility in an effort to hurt, annoy or upset, particularly among women.
catty.definition_1: Resembling or characteristic of a cat.

untie.definition_0: To loosen, as something interlaced or knotted; to disengage the parts of.
untie.definition_1: To free from fastening or from restraint; to let loose; to unbind.
untie.definition_2: To resolve; to unfold; to clear.

login.definition_0: A combination of a user's identification and password used to enter a computer, program, network, etc.

aorta.definition_0: The great artery which carries the blood from the heart to all parts of the body except the lungs; the main trunk of the arterial system.

rural.definition_0: A person from the countryside; a rustic.

artsy.definition_0: (sometimes derogatory) Inclined towards the arts; arty.

scram.definition_0: Leave in a hurry, go away.

guard.definition_0: A person who, or thing that, protects or watches over something.
guard.definition_2: A squad responsible for protecting something.

tonal.definition_0: Of or relating to tones or tonality.
tonal.definition_1: Of or relating to the general character, mood, or trend of something.
tonal.definition_2: Employing tones that have a predictable relationship to some tonic.

snowy.definition_0: Marked by snow, characterized by snow.
snowy.definition_2: Snow-white in color, white as snow.

leach.definition_0: A quantity of wood ashes, through which water passes, and thus imbibes the alkali.
leach.definition_1: A tub or vat for leaching ashes, bark, etc.
leach.definition_2: A jelly-like sweetmeat popular in the fifteenth century.

hound.definition_0: A dog, particularly a breed with a good sense of smell developed for hunting other animals.

going.definition_1: (chiefly of a machine) To work or function (properly); to move or perform (as required).
going.definition_2: To start; to begin (an action or process).

hence.definition_0: From here, from this place, away
hence.definition_1: From the living or from this world
hence.definition_2: (of a length of time) in the future from now

gecko.definition_0: Any lizard of the family Gekkonidae. They are small, carnivorous, mostly nocturnal animals with large eyes and adhesive toes enabling them to climb on vertical and upside-down surfaces.

condo.definition_0: Joint sovereignty over a territory by two or more countries.
condo.definition_1: A region or territory under such rule.
condo.definition_2: A building in which each unit is owned by an individual but the grounds, structure etc are owned jointly.

vaunt.definition_0: A boast; an instance of vaunting.

steer.definition_0: A suggestion about a course of action.

scamp.definition_0: A rascal, swindler, or rogue; a ne'er-do-well.
scamp.definition_1: A mischievous person, especially a playful, impish youngster.

skirt.definition_0: An article of clothing, usually worn by women and girls, that hangs from the waist and covers the lower part of the body.
skirt.definition_1: The part of a dress or robe, etc., that hangs below the waist.
skirt.definition_2: A loose edging to any part of a dress.

roger.definition_0: (radio telecommunications) Received (used in radio communications to acknowledge that a message has been received and understood)

adapt.definition_0: To make suitable; to make to correspond; to fit or suit
adapt.definition_1: To fit by alteration; to modify or remodel for a different purpose; to adjust
adapt.definition_2: To make by altering or fitting something else; to produce by change of form or character

organ.definition_0: A larger part of an organism, composed of tissues that perform similar functions.
organ.definition_1: (by extension) A body of an organization dedicated to the performing of certain functions.
organ.definition_2: A musical instrument that has multiple pipes which play when a key is pressed (the pipe organ), or an electronic instrument designed to replicate such.

feral.definition_0: A domesticated animal that has returned to the wild; an animal, particularly a domesticated animal, living independently of humans.
feral.definition_1: A contemptible young person, a lout, a person who behaves wildly.
feral.definition_2: A person who has isolated themselves from the outside world; one living an alternative lifestyle.

refit.definition_0: The process of having something fitted again, repaired or restored.

riser.definition_1: A platform or stand used to lift or elevate something.
riser.definition_2: The vertical part of a step on a staircase.

adult.definition_0: A fully grown human or animal.
adult.definition_1: A person who has reached the legal age of majority.

shave.definition_0: To make bald or shorter by using a tool such as a razor or pair of electric clippers to cut the hair close to the skin.
shave.definition_1: To cut anything in this fashion.
shave.definition_2: To remove hair from one's face by this means.
